volumes.desc: With a fresh update to the series, Ernie Lake brings Dance & Pop Vol 8. Sprinkled with his signature coy rhythms and glossy synth-work, these driving, sophisticated tracks have a european air and modern edge that will hook you right away. Check the urban glide and dusty flamenco guitar on "San Tan", "Click Clak" features shimmering synths and ethereal, syncopated grooves. Keen production gives the sparkling tracks found on Dance & Pop Vol 8 a taut edge and the modern, compelling rhythms will add dynamic tension and color to any situation.

volumes.title: Classic Jazz Vol 3
volumes.desc:
New Composer Mark Allaway brings delightful, tranquil melodies to Classic Jazz Vol 3. Featuring astute ragtimey guitar and sweet clarinet leads, one half solo and the other backed by a gentle bass and drum, this collection really shines! Check out
"Blues For Bilbo"- the clarinet and guitar follow the melody together winding together on a charming, subtle melody framed perfectly by the easy rhythm section. Alone, together on the lilting, "On Our Way" they stroll cheerfully through a happy, laid-back melody. The subtle hints of ragtime on "Ragtime Andy"
and the gypsy guitars  flavor the sweet jumping melody, but the band is calmly, gently wailing. This is a really excellent set and the production is is lovingly done, Classic Jazz Vol 3 will really set the mood.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 1
volumes.desc:
DJ Mar N Dean, the producers behind the Electrofied series, added new flavors and textures with Cinematic Electronic Vol 1
and Electric Love Vol 1, they continue to grow and take on more sonic palettes with Hip Hop Fused Vol 1. With an ear for the dense rhythmic soundscapes of techno, DJ Dean envelopes his hip hop beats with echoing, processed samples, subtle arpeggio synth lines, and swirling fields of synth pads, check "Bring It On" -it's trash can snare is twisted up with scratching samples and wicked effects while a smokey sitar floats above. A processed piano sample adds an old school feel to the 
stutter step of "Changes Happen". On "lifestyles" a hip-shaking, splattered snare bangs under a funky sax-like sample accented by hypnotic synth textures. The punchy hip hop beats give an urban anchor to the atmospheric synth-work on Hip Hop Fusion Vol 1, and really set this collection apart from the norm. These engaging textures and inventive beats will rock your body, and your mind.

volumes.title: Punk And Pop Vol 1
volumes.desc:
New composer Michele Vanni passionate and propulsive compositions are key to Punk And Pop Vol 1, emotive melodies and motivational rhythms abound, dig the jamming "Lets Party" 
joyous, rocking riffs and pounding drums keep the joint jumping.
"Cypher" is a grinding mosh pit rocker with an amazing guttural bass riff that will blow your mind and speakers. "Wild Journey" is a heartfelt acoustic guitar jangle with a wonderful warmth and a winsome melody. Great production keeps the explosive dynamics of the band real without crushing the instruments into a wall of noise. The compelling rhythms found on Punk And Pop vol 1 are sure to get the blood pumping, and the impassioned and dynamic guitars are sure to add a rocking edge to any situation.

volumes.title: Rock Fused Vol 1
volumes.desc:
DJ Mar And Dean bring you "Rock Fused Vol 1", a smoldering, funky, driving and dynamic new set of tracks. Dance textures underlie the grooving syncopated rhythms, tensed up with rock and roll structures. Acoustic and electric guitars adding the rock dynamic are effected and sampled, almost sounding like synths at times. Check out the cinematic drive of "Aggression"-
the propulsive beats are accented by sparkling acoustic guitars, adding a sunny sheen to the motivational groove. 
"Driving To Nowhere" is another stand-out, a haunting groove with a slinking rhythm and ghostly effects. "Mood Swing" is a full on rocker with syncopated snared driving a snarling guitar 
with road warrior abandon. Mar and Dean's explosive dynamics, hard hitting rhythms and cinematic pulse are key to Rock Fused Vol 1, and it's fresh, rocking tracks will update any atmosphere.

volumes.title: Digital Drive Vol 1
volumes.desc: New Composer Dave Greendale's focused compositions and his feel for a hook are key features to the dynamic tracks found on Digital Drive Vol 1, his sophisticated coloring and propulsive rhythms adding flash and motivation. On "Inspiring" swirling atmospheric synth pads float over a streamlined beat like clouds flying past an airplane window. "Coping With Pressure" is an aggressive on-the-edge track featuring robotic synths and an eerie sampled voice clashing over a pummeling machine beat. The ominous, oppressive synth pads of "Battle Ready" accent the stern, punchy rhythms, weaving a propulsive and threatening vibe. The vibrant tracks on Digital Drive Vol 1 will quicken the pulse, catch the ear and provide dynamic and driving soundscapes that will get you moving.

volumes.title: Digital Dreaming Vol 1
volumes.desc: Dave Greendale's enigmatic synth work on Digital Dreaming Vol 1 is key to the abstract sound-scapes he weaves. Utilizing effects and atmospheric synth pads he makes these tracks feel cavernous and spatially open, lending to a feeling of gently floating (or sinking) through space. The echoing, earthy rhythms of "Desert Caravan" take you on an arid, yet soulful glide beneath sun-drenched synth pads. Sparkling, underwater atmospherics swirl around a spongy synth melody on "Coral Reef". A murky drum machine fades in from behind an exotic wall of swirling synths on "Into The Depths" only to fade beneath the sonic haze. Delicate, yet engrossing, Digital Dreaming Vol 1 is a cinematic set of sonic backdrops sure to add a gentle hue and warming vibes to any scene.

volumes.title: Rock Grooves Vol 3
volumes.desc:
Dave Greendale works with a full band for Rock Grooves Vol 3
with great results- a powerful rhythm section is complimented by hefty guitars and excellent synth-work and tied up nicely by dynamic melodies and lovely production. Check the winsome Americana of "Prairie Dog"- a sweetly soloing electric plays a ringing lead over rustic acoustic guitar and an earthy rhythm section. "Maximum Limit"'s grungy guitars work dirty riffs over a dark, driving rhythm section with rock and roll determination.
"Take That" is some yummy powerpop with fuzzed up synths, distorto-guitars and fun anthemic feel. From moody ("It Cannot Be True") to funky ("Right As Ever") there are a lot of moods to explore on Rock Grooves Vol 3- and the sparkling production and hard hitting dynamics will add flash to any scene.

volumes.title: Instrumental Visions Vol 1
volumes.desc: Dave Greendale brings flavors from all over the world to the cinematic Instrumental Visions Vol 1, excellent musicianship, rustic, dramatic melodies and effortless charm are key features of this delightful melange. Dig the sprightly gypsy guitars trading licks on "French Quarter", "El Rancho" brings you a proud, steamy flamenco guitar, "Lush" is a smokey solo for sax accented by a sly chorded electric guitar. The instruments are played with love and joy on "Instrumental Visions Vol 1" and it shines through on tracks like "Washboard Jam"- a rollicking hey ride of a song. These picturesque tracks will frame and enrich any situation.

volumes.title: Digital World Vol 1
volumes.desc:
Dave Greendale has a more exotic and electronic take on world music for Digital World Vol 1, featuring sultry sambas, dynamic earthy percussion, and exotic melodies this is an attention grabbing set of tracks! "Bring A Bottle" is happy' flowing beach party jam with marimba and guitar weaving a syncopated melody that shines like the sun, "Idyllic Place" is a charming samba with a sparkling acoustic lead that will warm your heart.
"Gazelle" is a easy-swaying African influenced track with kalimba and soulful guitar weaving a delightful groove. Charming and upbeat melodies abound on Digital World Vol 1, these tracks will bring you to that special, calm space filled with warmth and positive vibrations!

volumes.title: Frequency  Orchestra Holiday Music Vol 1
volumes.desc: Just in time for the upcoming holiday season Freeplay brings you Frequency  Orchestral Holiday Music Vol 1, with arrangements by Dave Greendale, this collection features a heartwarming full vocal ensemble singing holiday favorites such as: "O Come All Ye Faithful" and "Ding Dong Merrily On High". The choir is wonderfully recorded and rings out with holiday spirit! Bells and glockenspiel weave the charmed melody of "Silent Night" with delicate joy. "The Holly And The Ivy" features flowing horns and flute weaving a stately, wintery tune.  Frequency  Orchestral Holiday Music Vol 1 is a delightful set of holiday favorites sure to warm your soul and fill your day with joy!

volumes.title: Orchestral Soundscapes Vol 4
volumes.desc:
New composer Patrick Smith brings vibrant, cinematic 
orchestral works to Orchestral Soundscapes Vol 4, dynamic moods and graceful textures fill these tracks with filmic possibilities! Check the purposeful pulse of "American At Heart" the heroic horn melody brimming with optimism over an industrious, driving rhythm.  Chiming percussion sparkles like stars amid the flowing strings of "Distant Oceans", the colorful piece sways with a dreamy fluid grace. "Flagship Commander" bursts from the fog as the orchestra scales grand heights of the imagination. Orchestral Soundscapes Vol 4 brings you fluid, graceful and forceful moods that will set the stage with emotion and power.

volumes.title: Tech Grooves Vol 5
volumes.desc:
New composer Rick Balentine brings a funk edge to the dynamic electronic compositions on Tech Grooves Vol 5, boisterous bass playing and raw, dirty drums give a dynamic tension and punch to the edgy tracks. Dig the dj scratch effected groove of "Round The Block"- the whole track stops and starts-  giving a physical feel to the hook. "Crimson Red" has a definite prog feel- it's funky, dirty synths churning and flowing- the jungle rhythm bubbling like a stew. "What Is This" is a hot, burning, funk psychedelia with a gutter guitar riff and a pounding snare weaving a sweaty rhythm. Tech Groove Vol 5 brings you punchy, dynamic grooves featuring fat bass riffing and powerful drumming, these hot tracks will provide a soulful
edge to any scene!

volumes.title: Digital Drive Vol 2
volumes.desc: Composer Dave Greendale brings moody grooves and warm, emotive synths to Digital Drive Vol 2. Focused rhythms and spot-on melodies are key to these atmospheric tracks, check out the fingered bass and soulful electric piano of "Hiding Place"- weaving an earthy melody over a moody, driving snare. "Cruel Taunts" features tweaked, glitched beats and a fat, dirty bass riff, the track turns the funk up when the snare drops in. The atmospheric "Beneath The Waves" has a warm, hazy feel generated by hypnotic synth pads, it's subtle beats have an easy drive. Digital Drive Vol 2 is a lush collection of pulsing electronica tracks sure to add glowing, emotive textures to any scene.

volumes.title: Rock Grooves Vol 4
volumes.desc:
Composers Loeffler and Wolfert bring you rich, Americana flavors and and easy rocking tracks with Rock Grooves Vol 4. 
From the hard edged, L.A. style push of "Drivin Nowhere" to the down home stomp of "Rock To Roll" dynamic melodies and upbeat vibes abound. "Rocking Out To The Radio" features a warm sunny disposition and a groovy AM radio vibe, "Memories Of The Past" is a winsome, charming Americana track with a loving melody. The senic, colorful guitars are key to the dynamic tracks found on Rock Grooves Vol 4 and will bring a dynamic and effective feel to any situation.

volumes.title: TV Themes Vol 2
volumes.desc:
Updating and re-energizing our themes series, composers Loeffler and Wolfert bring you dynamic orchestral rock news tags and slamming sports tracks featuring bold melodies and motivational rhythms. Dig the serious, propulsive energy of "News Room Drama" for a hard hitting, action packed vibe.
"Opening Theme" is a sports tag with heroic horns and grinding guitars over a heart-racing beat. "Full Force Battle" features dramatic, orchestral accents with an urgent, forcefull pulse.
If you are looking for serious, driving news themes or heroic sports tags, please check out TV Themes Vol 2.

volumes.title: Digital Drive Vol 3
volumes.desc:
Composer Dave Greendale's driving, modern rhythms are key to the dynamic tracks on Digital Drive Vol 3, propulsive, but never heavy handed, his intelligent beats are enhanced by warm melodies and ear-catching hooks-  check the fab "Hallucination"
where warm belled synths work a happy melody over a poppy, energetic beat. Sonic synths bring "Guerrilla Force" a darker feel but the pushing, motivational beats still get you moving.
Slamming snares and hooky melodies abound on Digital Drive Vol 3, a dynamic set sure to put some flash and bang into any project.

volumes.title: Industrial Dimensions Vol 1
volumes.desc: Composer Patrick James Slattery (of Dark Dimensions Vols 1,3,4 & 5) gives his amazing sonic soundscapes a more rhythmic turn for Industrial Dimensions Vol 1, and adds a fantastic ethnic female vocal to a few tracks as well. Dig the menacing, aggressive push of "Evil Is Near," featuring amazing ringing noises and skull crushing double kick beats. "Crossing Over" brings lovely, exotic vocals floating over ethereal atmospheres. Furious double kicks lead the cinematic "Machines Rebelling" accented by intense sound-fields with sonically mesmerizing results. Industrial Dimensions Vol 1 will add tense and dynamic ambience to any situation.

volumes.title: Industrial Ambience Vol 1
volumes.desc:
Composer Patrick James Slattery uses tape manipulation, effects and synths to build amazing, cinematic sonic atmospheres for Industrial Ambience Vol 1, darker and more dynamic than ambient, the stunning pieces weave hellish tension and thunderous clamoring into wicked aural landscapes. The  bone chilling vibration of "Rusted Hull" oppresses and envelopes you like a dense murderous fog. The demonic drawn-out bass rattles of Stagnant Chill will make your skin crawl. Metallic echoes slip across the stereo-field over the tense growling atmosphere of "Remote Location" like sonic ghosts.
The amazing sonic landscapes on Industrial Ambience Vol 1 weave a palpable tension that will capture and enrich your imagination.

volumes.title: Rocked Up Vol 7
volumes.desc:
Composer Darko Saric brings ear catching hooks, warm melodies and a solid back-up band to Rocked Up Vol 7, evoking happy memories and signaling good times, his upbeat tracks shine.
Dig the tremolo guitars and sexy glide of "Beachcombing"-
it's wistful glow like a setting sun. "Feeling Alright" is a perfect soundtrack for an afternoon drive, with sparkling guitars like sun flashing through the leaves. Rocked Up Vol 7 is a dynamic set of happy rocking tracks that will bring a sunny vibe to any scene.

volumes.title: Moods And Grooves Vol 7
volumes.desc: Composers Loeffler and Wolfert bring inspired and inventive melodies and dynamics to Moods And Grooves Vol 7, employing energizing skills to cover a broad range of genres, these cinematic tracks swing from a happy Latin jam "Latin Gathering, to a tense cinematic thriller "Spy Undercover. "Morning After The Storm" features a dramatic piano and string melody over an ephemeral rhythm with a heartbeat pulse. The refreshing and skillful musicianship is captured perfectly, giving Moods And Grooves Vol 7 a charismatic shine that will add drive and polish to any scene.

volumes.title: Bangin Beats Vol 3
volumes.desc: New composer Raymond Rodriguez brings sneaky, streetwise beats to Bangin Beats Vol 3. Featuring moody synths and deep bass these gritty tracks ooze with dark vibes, dig the funk fueled horn samples on "Hands Up" pumping up a dirty machine drum, "Soldier Mission" has dramatic stringed synths ringing out over a sullen urban landscape of beats and bass. Bangin Beats Vol 3 will add head- nodding textures and dark, mysterious vibes to any situation.

volumes.title: Digital Drive Vol 4
volumes.desc: Dave Greendale brings an ear for detail and a captivating sense of melody to Digital Drive Vol 4, establishing the hooks with syncopated accents, pulsing synths and dynamic rhythms. Check the driving drum machine on "West Coast Style,"  its pulse compelling a stand-up bass and piano melody with future jazz results. A strange and warped orchestra leads "Unusual Happenings" careening along over a gliding synth beat, all together a spooky, fascinating track. "New Guru" is an exotic stomp with a fiery, world-beat vibe and swirling, mesmerizing melodies. The lush synths and dynamic rhythms on Digital Drive Vol 4 are attention grabbing elements that will capture and captivate your ears and soul.

volumes.title: FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Bruch Violin Concerto 1
volumes.desc: Frequency Orchestra brings you Max Bruch's most acclaimed romantic piece, his first violin concerto. Impassioned and fantastic violin lines shine over the grand and sweeping orchestra in what has been called the greatest work in the Romantic tradition. Dave Greendale's tight production lets the dynamic orchestra sing. FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Bruch Violin Concerto 1 is an amazing work that will fill your soul and awaken your spitits with grand and eloquent emotion.

volumes.title:
FREQUENCY Onsions Vol 1 will add tense and dynamic ambience to any situation.


 Dec, 17, 2007 -
FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Nocturnes
volumes.desc:
Chopin's elegant nocturnes inspire emotions beyond words, Freeplay is delighted to bring you these superlative works for solo piano with FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Nocturnes, "Nocturne Opus 9 No 2" is a thoughtful piece brimming with love for the piano and the melodies it weaves, exploring it's facets and hues with the joy of finding and learning. "Nocturne Opus 15 No 2" is a loving,
romantic lulaby with a warmth and understanding that stirs the spirit. Chopin's nocturnes are lovingly produced with Dave Greendale's gentle touch and the exemplary piano playing sparkles with dynamics and emotion. "FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Nocturnes" features magnificent, important music, masterfully done.

volumes.title: FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Delibes Selections
volumes.desc:
French composer Leo Delibes is most famous for his operatic works, childrens music and waltzes, Frequency Orchestra brings you some of each - The Flower Duet" from "Lakme" is a rustic duet for female voices with an urgent and spiritual feel, "Sylvia Pizzicato" is a cute tune featuring pizzicato strings and a cartoon-like dynamic. "Coppelia Prelude and Mazurka" is a whirling Polish dance with wintery orchestral fireworks, The "Waltz from Coppelia" is an elegant and ornamental waltz with a delightful cadence and form.
The rustic, emotive selections found on FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Delibes Selections will inspire and warm every audience.

volumes.title: FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Polonaise
volumes.desc:
Chopin's compositions for piano shine with his virtuosic love for the instrument, diving into the vigorous, rolling key work like a gardener digging into the most fertile of soils. These selections, Polonaise and other studies,
bring you dynamics and emotion from Nature - (Winter Wind Opus 25), Love - (Etude Tristesse Opus 10) and the piano itself- (Black Keys Study), executed beautifully and in lovely fidelity. FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Polonaise is another delightful volume that will expand your horizons and bring color to a dreary winters day.

volumes.title: FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Piano Concerto 2
volumes.desc: Comprising themes from previous Nocturnes and composed when Chopin was 20 years old this peerless concerto is full of ache and ambition. With it's virtuosic piano arpeggios and cinematic string atmospheres this fantastic concerto brings dynamic crescendos and ruminative ornamentation. The amazing performance is captured warmly by Dave Greendale's excellent production. FREQUENCY ORCHESTRA: Chopin Piano Concerto 2 is another spectacular orchestral work that will add depth and dimension to any project.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Bach Brandenburg 1 and 2
volumes.desc: A vibrant, elegant air percolates through Bach's unsurpassable Brandenburg Concertos, featuring colorful polyphonic ornaments and complex, dramatic counterpoint. Bach entwines intricate melodies with sonorous, living rhythms with a fearless joy and this delightful collection will add charm and confidence to any situation, Frequency Orchestra is proud to add Bach Brandenburg Concertos 1 and 2 to the collection.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Bach Brandenburg 3 and 4
volumes.desc: Deeper into the concertos, the first of these 2 works features virtuosic violin lines and a minimal architecture that may have been an invitation for improvisation. The second features very complex harpsichord lines and contrapuntal textures.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Bach Brandenburg 5 and 6
volumes.desc:
Completing the series of delightful and dynamic Baroque works with
Frequency Orch. Bach Brandenburg 5 and 6, we bring you a virtuosic performance brought to life by Dave Greendale's majestic production. These wonderful works will add a divine presence and period piece dynamics to any project.

volumes.title: Sports Power Vol 1
volumes.desc: Dynamic composer Ben Kopec's raging, industrial soundscapes lead Sports Power Vol 1, this motivational volume brings impact and flash with powerful vocals, pounding beats and stone cold shredding guitars. Check the great rhythmic hooks in "Slick Slider" where the guitar's echo with the vocal adds a cool pulsing texture to the driving chorus. "Body Slam" is a skull rattling groove with an unrelenting push. "Open Up" features a bombastic drive that pushes the pulse to the limit with nonstop action and aggression. The robust mix brings the guitars and drums crisp and in your face, the fast and furious dynamics on Sports Power Vol 1 will add bone crunching dynamics to any situation.

volumes.title: Sunny Summer Rock Vol 3
volumes.desc:
Composer Joi Veer (American Standards Vols 1 & 2, Sunny Summer Rock Vol 1) is back with a  shiny new set of summer rock tracks to pick you up and get you smiling!  His warm and easy guitars, driving pop rhythms and sparkling synths weave upbeat and motivational melodies with toe-tapping grace.
Check the hazy glide of "On The Go" for an effortless pop groove with rich melodies and a warm, happy outlook.  "Zig-A-Dig Song" features a hilarious vocal
line over a sunny pop rhythm. Joi Veer gracefully combines fun and warming melodies with solid rock and pop rhythms for dynamic and cheery tracks, his flawless production brings professional shine and his sunny outlook  flavors this delightful set! Sunny Summer Rock Vol 3 will wash away the grey and brighten up your day!

volumes.title: Rock Fused Vol 2
volumes.desc: Composer's DJ Mar And Dean bring a fresh update to the Fused collections with Rock Fused Vol 2, These cinematic tracks feature driving beats and psychedelic flavors spun by effected guitars. Dig the enigmatic "A Road Leading Home", featuring  an effected acoustic/electric guitar that weaves an exotic, unworldly melody, with string fingerings that sound sitar-like, as a plainitive, driving rhythm pulses and throbs underneath. "Only Regrets" has an mysterious, earthy world-beat that runs beneith an exotic atmosphere of echoing guitar effects, shakers and ringing guitar lines. Rock Fused Vol 2 is another excellent set of tracks from the dynamic DJ Mar And Dean! these tracks will add flash, drive, and cutting edge atmospheres to any situation.

volumes.title: Dark Drones Vol 1
volumes.desc:
Composer Pete Calandra delivers an intense and filmic set of tracks for Dark Drones Vol 1, dark, spectral atmospheric pieces featuring ominous 
colors and foreboding chills with cinematic flair. "In The Mist" features a fearful, humid atmosphere pierced by wraithlike stringed synths, "Dark Time's" piano tinkles wander a forlorn electric landscape battered by ghostlike synth winds. "Red Moon" is a tense, building piece featuring gurgling, dark bass noises and effected foghorn synths weaving an unwelcoming vibe. The subtle and oppressive qualities of Dark Drones Vol 1 will bring intense and dark atmospheres to any production with cinematic impact and subtle mystery.

volumes.title: Bangin Beats Vol 4
volumes.desc: Composer Kelley Kelley, who brought you the first volume of Bangin Beats refreshes his catalogue with this excellent new set, fresh sounds and killer effects are key to the punchy mixes and dynamic tracks found on Bangin Beats Vol 4. Dig the sweaty funk and bombastic grind of "Lady Demeanor" featuring a wacked guitar line and fat bass thumps. "About To Jump" is an omnious track with spooky synths and a dark, driving attitude. Edgy, pushy and dark, these dynamic tracks will add grit to your projects as well as a streetwise pulse.

volumes.title: Frequency Orchestra Dvorak New World Symphony
volumes.desc: Dvorak's marvelous New World Symphony was composed during a stay in the U.S. just at the close of the 19th century, this work speaks of change, growth and enterprise. Influenced by the melting pot of America, Dvorak references multinational folk melodies in his use of the pentatonic scale in this triumphant, diverse work. Dave Greendale's excellent production gives the dynamic orchestra verve and shine, bringing you right to the center of Dvorak's stratospheric symphony.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Elgar Pomp and Circumstance
volumes.desc:
Composer Edward Elgar's renowned Pomp And Circumstance marches are patriotic odes to England and proud banners of martial ceremony but, beyond that, they are charming and warm pieces full of dashing exuberance and regal grace. The Marches have become part of England's national repertoire with Movement No.1 featuring, "Land Of Hope And Glory", played every year at the world famous, "Last Night Of The Proms". From elegant waltzing sections to massive horn climaxes, the grit and clash of battle and the gleam of sun on steel are portrayed with a grand architecture of melody. The Frequency Orchestra and Dave Greendale are proud to present Elgar's
heroic marches, Opus 39, Pomp And Circumstance.

volumes.title: Music For Pictures Vol 9
volumes.desc: Prolific Composer David Flavin (Music For Pictures Vols. 3,6,8, Sunny Summer Rock Vol 2 and Moods And Grooves Vol 6) is back with a dynamic set of cinematic tracks on Music For Pictures Vol 9. Bringing you tense atmospheres, lost melodies and ominous rhythms, this dark volume will add spooky elements and taut feelings with excellent effect. Check "Difficult To Breathe"- an obstinate bell melody builds a tense atmosphere, shot through with nervous strings and pensive rhythms. On "Betrayal Of A Friend" the title explains exactly the feel of the song- a gothic chorus breathes hellfire as dark robotic beats add a turgid rhythm to the unsettling and dark melody. Music For Pictures Vol 9 is a dark and claustrophobic volume that will add evil textures and oppressive atmospheres to your projects with unearthly aplomb.

volumes.title: Electronic Fused Vol 1
volumes.desc: Composers DJ Mar And Dean bring you the third installment of the Fused series with this wicked new experimental set; Electronic Fused Vol 1, featuring moody soundscapes, fluid, panoramic rhythms and really amazing synth work. Mar and Dean raise the bar with this release, dig the enigmatic rhythms of "Industrial Sector"- glitched out beats crackle with syncopated grooves as dense computer synths weave futuristic atmospheres. The oddly upbeat "Elliptical Revolution " features a stepping street beat and A Haystack" features a smooth, spacey hip hop that evokes the feel of a city drive at night. A hardcore oldschool vibe can be found on "The News," which pits the seedy growl of dual vocals against fat, grainy horn stabs. Meanwhile, "Alone in Da Graveyard" has an anxious vibe, morphing and floating with the whispers of synths and electronic effects. Don't miss "Nightmare in A-Minor" for a hefty dose authentic, thoroughbred street action that will steal the show.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 2
volumes.desc:
Updating the Hip Hip Fused series DJ Mar And Dean hit you with some laid back grooves and sneaky beats on Hip Hop Fused Vol 2. With light flavors of funk and humid synth pad atmospheres their space age melodies give you a bit of a lounge feel over easy grooving, streetwise beats. Dig the cinematic, simmering "Take Off"- it's bubbling synths feel as if you were gliding along with the mellow beat across blue skies. The belled synths of "West Side Of Town" give the  melody a spacey, cinematic atmosphere as a slow groove simmers underneath.
The easy gliding tracks found on Hip Hop Fused Vol 2 will bring rhythmic textures and heady synth atmospheres to your projects, click the link above to check it out!

volumes.title: Action And Adventure Vol 1
volumes.desc: Freeplay brings you Action And Adventure Vol 1, picture perfect, driving tracks that will add dynamic rhythms and tense emotions to your project or surroundings. Dig the intense push of "Army Angels" with thundering orchestral horns laying aggressive lines over a driving machine beat. "Face To Face" features no-nonsense rhythms pushing orchestral horns to the limit, spacey breaks hi-lited by flutes give you a breather before the driving beats kick back in. This cinematic set of tracks will add gusto and aggressive dynamics to any situation, with might and drive.

volumes.title: Cinematic Electronic Vol 3
volumes.desc: Cinematic Electronic Vol 3 is a fantastic new set of dark, atmospheric tracks featuring orchestral instruments (horns, percussion, strings) weaving taught atmospheres over effected drumbox beats and topped off by dark, mysterious synth accents. Combining the organic and synthesized elements adds an eerie edge to these tense and dynamic pieces. "Keep Cool" features a throbbing bass and echoing synth beats that build and push but never quite explode, leaving the listener on the edge of his seat. "Temptation Place" has a sneaky beat and percussion accents that give a hide and seek thrill to the spooky synths. This simmering, shadowy set of dark tracks will flesh out elements of suspense in your project. Click the link above to check it out!

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Grieg Suites and Marches
volumes.desc:
Freeplay and the Frequency orchestra are proud to present this masterful selection of suites and marches from the composer Grieg, wonderful string melodies are key to this collection, The Morning Mood Suite from Peer Gynt
is a quintessental picturesque piece with it's gentle, sonorous tones. "Holberg Suite (Prelude)" is a rousing, emotionally overflowing piece with soaring melodies. Grieg Suites and Marches is an unabashed and melodious set that will bring gracefull and spirited moods into your day and into your soul.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Grieg Piano Concerto 1
volumes.desc: Grieg's magnificent first concerto for piano sings with an unbridled joy for life. Elegant, sophisticated piano lines lead the vivid orchestra through complex and engaging emotions from lilting meditation to feverish passion. The incisive orchestra brings this dynamic work to life with a passion that will breathe heady life into any project.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Glinka Overture
volumes.desc: Glinka's Russlan and Ludmilla Overture twinkles with a charming, lighthearted brilliance. This popular work bounds with joy and leaps to soaring grand heights. Dave Greendale captures the electric piece in all it's glory. Sure to bring sweeping power to any scene.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Faure Requiem
volumes.desc: Composer Gabriel Faure brings a delightful love and light to this enriching volume, featuring flowing choral polyphony and emotional string and organ accompaniment, this magnificent recording gently weaves peaceful melodies and meditative voices with spiritual joy. Click the link above to stream or download these dramatic tracks now!

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Handel Organ Concerto 13
volumes.desc: Frequency Orchestra is proud to present Handels engaging 13th concerto for organ, altho scored for small group including oboe, strings and bass section the energetic and robust melodies take it beyond just baroque, at times dizzying and careening, saintly and focused at others. Sparkling and overflowing with joy this witty and enigmatic volume with delight you with it's vivid presence.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Handel Messiah
volumes.desc: Perhaps the most well known vocal choral in the western world, Handel's Messiah, is brought to vivid life by Dave Greendale and the Frequency Orchestra. This rousing, passonate choral breathes with an exalting light of love and joy. Rising to glorious heights and brimming with emotive melodies, this shining set will fill you with spiritual peace.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Handel Harp Concerto
volumes.desc: Handel's concerto for harp is an elegant and confident work. It's paired down orchestra and demure, efficent harp lines are modest but, there is beauty in the unfussy harp playing, and the subordinate orchestra seems to color in all the right parts with a sublime brush. This forthright and lovely work will bring a sophisticated sparkle and shimmer to any scene.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Handel Water Music Suite
volumes.desc: Freeplay is proud to present Dave Greedale's splendid arrangement for Handel's Water Music Suite. With the excellent production we've grown accustomed to, this magnificent work shines with clarity and musicianship. Handel's Water Music was written for King George, to be played on the royal barge, so you will find delightful baroque pieces with regal bearing and grand designs. This cinematic Suite has no real order because the louder songs were to be played when the barge drifted away from the King's boat and the quieter parts when it got closer, with that in mind, please enrich your day by clicking on the above link to enjoy Handel's masterful classical work.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Handel Overture and Minuet
volumes.desc: Wrapping up our Handel selection, Freeplay and the Frequency Orchestra bring you this diverse and masterful collection of Handel's works. From the elegatic, meditative "Minuet (from Berenice)" to the dynamic, triumphant "Overture (from Julius Caesar)" this excellent compilation brings you from rumination to exaltation. Dave Greendale guides the orchestral production with a genuine and reverent hand, bringing you unparalled sound and dynamics. This exemplary collection brings a myriad of professional and emotional flavors that will enhance any production or project.

volumes.title: Action And Adventure Vol 2
volumes.desc:
Freeplay brings you Action And Adventure Vol 2, a dynamic set of pulse raising tracks featuring orchestral elements, ethnic percussion and oud. "Cairo Chase" is a fast-paced, razor edged jam featuring rapid fire dohol drumming and punctuating oud, with bombastic horns adding a scary forcefulness. "Free People"
brings flute, strings and voice swelling into a single golden-hued sound, warming and rising like a sunrise, with an amazing enchanting feel. "Warriors Arise!" is a churning, epic piece with a demonic, vocal chorus, slashing percussion and throbbing horn lines. Action And Adventure Vol 2 is a vivid set of tracks ranging from epic fantasy to simmering suspense that will add flash and pulse to any scene.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Grieg Suites and Marches
Battle Themes Vol 1
volumes.desc: Epic, agressive high impact tracks are featured on Battle Themes Vol 1, harsh, resounding  horns, rapid-fire snares, thundering timpani and tense, keening string lines give punchy dynamics to these orchestral compositions. "Crawl And Hide" is a nightmarish suspense track that features military snares that twich like an itchy trigger finger and ringing strings riding a razor edge. Growling cellos weave an evil, tense atmosphere on "Lost Wars" with rolling timpani building like thunder, bursting the anxious atmosphere. Battle Themes Vol 1 epic and aggressive tracks will add a mighty flash and bang to enliven and punctuate your project.

volumes.title: Bossa Nova Vol 2
volumes.desc: Breezy, latin tracks are featured on Bossa Nova Vol 2, effortlessly lush melodies with enchanting beach moods and charming female vocal vamps. The syncopated clave hits on "Mediterranean" give a jazzy rhythm for piano, organ and horns to weave laid-back melodies with a jovial flow. "Mediation" features a delightful female vamp over a busy but sanguine rhtythm, 12 string guitar adds a enriching solo. This senic and sublime volume will flavor your day with easy stepping, upbeat atmospheres perfect for beach and summertime scenes.

volumes.title: Dark Dimensions Vol 6
volumes.desc:
Intense, dark and foreboding tracks are featured on Dark Dimensions Vol 6,
extreme, guttural bass noises and rasping, ghostly synths create evil and claustrophobic sound-scapes. Dig the tense, crouching strings on "Dark Awakening" -the decending string lines weave an anxious atmosphere as deep cello lines slither and growl. On "Muted Fear" dark strings develop a mournful melody as kettle drums echo in the distance like bombs, ghostly synth add evil, wispered noises. Dark Dimensions Vol 6 brings you harsh atmospheres that will add a fantastic edege to any evil project or dark scene.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Haydn Selections
volumes.desc: Frequency Orchestra is proud to present this delightful collection of Haydn's best works, featuring the beloved "Surprise Symphony". Haydn's deft and engaging compositional style is fleshed out by the gentle arrangement of Dave Greendale and the delightful orchestra brings these premere works to living, breathing life.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Berlioz Symphony Fantastic
volumes.desc: The Symphony Fantastic, is a romantic, free-thinking work that casts aside norms of the day for a ravishing and dynamic intensity. Featuring grand, sweeping codas and a waltz without a trio, this enigmatic composition speaks of a lovelorn suitor who's futile suicide attempt brings him to the brink of madness and beyond. Impassioned and entwined with the mystery of love, this amazing symphony will bring imaginative colors and broad, sweeping emotions to intrigue your mind and soul.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Holst The Planet Suite
volumes.desc: Written for a very large orchestra and featuring seven tone poems, Holst's Planet Suite is an ingenious work brimming with the fire of life and the mysticism of the mind. The Frequency Orchestra scales the thunderous highs and the melancholic lows of this prodigal work with verve and passion, bringing this enigmatic work to life. Please click the link above to enjoy this delightful and exemplary masterpiece.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Lizst Piano Concerto 1
volumes.desc: Written with the help of his pupil, Lizst's first concerto is a mercurial work featuring Lizst's octave-scaling piano chords. Ingenious weaving of themes throughout holds this work together and keeps the melody fresh. With lyrical dialogue and dramatic flair the orchestra and piano work off each other- sometimes cooperating and at others against, providing the crucial, dynamic spark that makes this concerto shine.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Lizst Piano Concerto 2
volumes.desc: The movments of this work flow together seamlessly so that Lizst's Piano Concerto 2 is more of a symphonic poem for piano, with it's theme morphing and veering over the piece with exuberant compositional skill. Equally profound and grandiloquent, this dynamic work will thrill and pacify as you listen to the theme as it comes to life and traces it's glorious colors throughout this engaging concerto.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Clarke Trumpet Voluntary
volumes.desc:
This elegant baroque masterpiece will delight you with it's filigreed charm,
radiant and swelling melodies and a regal beat make this brilliant track a wedding favorite. Please click the link above to bask in it's sunny warmth.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Dukas Sorcerers Apprentice
volumes.desc:
Dukas' best known work, The Sorcerers Apprentice, is a cinematic and dynamic scherzo. Vividly telling the story of an aspiring wizard, this colorful piece 
weaves  mystical melodies into a seething, towering explosion that conveys the tale with amazingly visual composition, coming alive before your eyes (and ears). The Frequency Orchestra shines on this exciting track  with dynamic clarity, as ever, Dave Greendale's warm production makes this magical work glow.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Leoncavallo Selections
volumes.desc: Featuring incredible vocal performances, Frequency Orch. brings you emotional and inspiring selections from Leoncavallo's operatic repertoire. "On With The Motley", from Il Pagliacci is a heart-wrenching, dramatic piece with a stunning solo voice. "Der Bajazzo" features a swelling and uplifting full chorus that scales dramatic heights with emotional and spiritual joy. Please click the above link to bring a little operatic drama to your day.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mouret Rondeau
volumes.desc: Brimming with the splendor and ostentation of Old England, Mouret's regal Rondeau, burns with an upright, patriotic gleam. The Frequency Orchestra delivers you a heroic and reverent version, guided by Dave Greendale's gentle production, sparkling with pomp and pride.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Massenet Meditation (from Thais)
volumes.desc: Filled with light and sacred love, the ethereal melodies of this loving hymnal caress and warm the soul. As Massenet's most successful composition, this sublime meditation stands alone with it's heavenly glow and gentle lilt. Please click the link above for a sweetly transcendental moment.

volumes.title: Modern Rock Vol 1
volumes.desc: Prolific composer Pete Calandra brings bright, positive vibes to his new collection "Modern Rock Vol 1", fresh, ringing guitars and subtle synths build progressive, natural melodies over a dynamic and effective rhythm section. Dig the upbeat, flashy pop-punk of "Dont Wink"- grinding guitars and propulsive drums make for a highly motivational groove, "This Is The Time" weaves dark melodies over an atmospheric rhythm for an expressive track with tense undertones. Modern Rock Vol 1 will add positive motivation to your project or your day, please click the link above for some excellent rock and roll.

volumes.title: Electronic Fused Vol 2
volumes.desc: DJ Mar N Dean are back with a volume of varied electronic music that ranges from the sweetly melodic to the darkly ambient.  Eclectic synth work and a wide range of tonal colors perfectly compliment the persistent beats.  Electronic Fused Vol 2 offers moody and atmospheric music that lends itself perfectly to a variety of projects.

volumes.title: World Symphonic Vol 1
volumes.desc: World Symphonic Vol 1 brings you orchestral works with an exotic, international flair, mixing modern elements with with strings and horns, refreshing the world music genre and bringing a weighty and emotive appeal to the style. World Symphonic Vol 1 is a dynaic set of tracks that will bring a captivating shine to your project and to your ears.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Italian Symphony
volumes.desc: This dramatic composition, Mendelssohn's Italian Symphony, features emotive and demonstrative strings on lead with a dynamic orchestral backing. From the joyous opening movement to the tarantella styled finale this engrossing work beats with positive emotions. The Frequency Orchestra and Freeplay Music are proud to present Mendelssohn's illuminating symphony, please click the link above to enjoy this edifying composition.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Scottish Symphony
volumes.desc: Mendelssohn's Scottish Symphony is a study in tension and drama as the music rises and falls with powerful dynamic shifts.  The melodies conjure up images of the stormy Highlands as the composition stays true to its name.  Mendelssohn's Scottish Symphony is an important piece of early Romantic music that leaves a definite impression on the listener and the Frequency Orchestra presents this piece in all of its dramatic glory.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Violin Concerto
volumes.desc: This wonderful Violin Concerto, composed by Felix Mendelssohn, showcases the abilities of the instrument in dramatic fashion.  The orchestra lends dynamic support without overpowering the expressive and agile violin.  The Frequency Orchestra's recording of Mendelssohn's Violin Concerto shows the impressive musical range of its title instrument through a faithful rendering of this dramatic concerto.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Selections
volumes.desc: These selections from the work of Felix Mendelssohn are two of the Romantic composer's most famous pieces.  The "Wedding March (from Midsummer Nights Dream)" is a true classic of the 19th century and is one of the best-known examples of Classical music.  The Frequency Orchestra performs these famous works with grace and ease as the brilliant compositions of Felix Mendelssohn are brought to life.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mahler Symphony 1
volumes.desc: Gustav Mahler's 1st Symphony is a dynamic and triumphant piece of late Romantic composition, full of strong strings and Herculean horns.  The piece runs the gamut of emotional expression, from mournful to triumphant, before reaching the glorious conclusion.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mahler's Symphony 1 is a powerful musical statement that leaves the listener dazed and awestruck.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 1
volumes.desc: This brilliant Piano Concerto, by Felix Mendelssohn, features impressively dexterous work from the title instrument as well as sweeping and tasteful orchestral accompaniment.  The piece opens intensely with a dramatic first movement which is contrasted perfectly by the soft, mid-tempo second movement, followed by a fierce and triumphant third movement which drives the piece to a close.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mendelssohn's Piano Concerto 1 is sure to satisfy the listener's craving for skilled piano-playing in an orchestral context.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 2
volumes.desc: Mendelssohn's 2nd Piano Concerto is full of power and passion.  The swift piano playing and elegant orchestral accompaniment compliment each other beautifully as the piece runs from fierce and fiery to soft and sweet.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mendelssohn's Piano Concerto 2 displays both skill and taste in this wonderful piece of early Romantic music.

volumes.title: Dark Dimensions Vol 8
volumes.desc: This collection of dark, ambient, electronic music features eerie orchestral accompaniment.  The tracks are tense and foreboding as ominous noise lies steadily underneath.  Dark Dimensions Vol 8 provides a ghostly atmosphere for any project in need of some gloom.

volumes.title: Mystical Symphonic Vol 1
volumes.desc: The orchestral arrangements of Mystical Symphonic Vol 1 conjure up images of timeless mystery.  Lush strings and dark horns give way to ethereal melodies in a highly cinematic manner.  Mystical Symphonic Vol 1 offers an atmosphere of Medieval mystery suitable for a variety of projects.

volumes.title: Cinematic Electronic Vol 4
volumes.desc: Cinematic Electronic Vol 4 features atmospheric electronic grooves and is full of warm synth and fluttering electronic drums.  The tracks range from driving and intense to smooth and relaxed, with organic instruments adding to the laid-back electronic grooves.  Cinematic Electronic Vol 4 is sure to enhance the mood of your project.

volumes.title: Mystical Symphonic Vol 2
volumes.desc: These soft, understated orchestral tracks are packed with lush strings and timeless melodies.  Echoes of Renaissance music abound as images of times of old are conveyed by the tasteful orchestral arrangements.  Mystical Symphonic Vol 2 offers a pastoral atmosphere that will lend your project an air of history.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Piano Concerto 21
volumes.desc: A classic work from one of the most important composers of all time, Mozart's Piano Concerto 21 is rhythmic and upbeat, but with a healthy amount of tension and drama.  The swift and lilting piano leads the piece, with buoyant orchestral accompaniment in support, and the Frequency Orchestra deftly executes the virtuosic composition.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mozart's Piano Concerto 21 is a joyous display of instrumental and compositional skill.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Violin Concerto 4
volumes.desc: Mozart's Violin Concerto 4 is a joyful piece that beautifully showcases the capabilities of the title instrument.  The violin weaves intricate melodies around the light orchestral accompaniment as the playful rhythms drive the piece forward.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mozart's Violin Concerto 4 is a joyous and rhythmic piece from one of history's great composers.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Violin Concerto 5
volumes.desc: This beautiful violin concerto by Mozart is full of lush orchestration and sweet melodies.  The violin plays cascading arpeggios as the orchestra sets the harmonic stage with poignant and playful melodies constantly emerging.  Mozart's Violin Concerto 5, as performed by the Frequency Orchestra, is a study in the expressive capabilities of the violin with tasteful orchestral accompaniment.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Horn Concerto 3
volumes.desc: The third Concerto for French horn, by Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart, tests the limits of the horn in both dexterity and expressivity.  The orchestra lends lush harmonic texture to the graceful horn lines as the piece dances with grace.  The Frequency Orchestra executes this composition wonderfully with special credit to the French horn player who performs the difficult music with both power and ease .  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Mozart's Horn Concerto 3 is sure to satisfy your desire for beautiful Classical music.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Horn Concerto 4
volumes.desc: Wolfgang Mozart's Horn Concerto 4 features buoyant strings and a subtly powerful  French horn throughout.  The luxurious and playful rhythms drive the piece as the French horn plays graceful melodies while enveloped by lush orchestral accompaniment.  Mozart's Horn Concerto 4, as performed by the Frequency Orchestra, exhibits the capabilities of the title instrument perfectly and is a wonderful example of Mozart's great compositional skills.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Flute Concerto 2
volumes.desc: Nimble flute and subtle strings abound in Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart's Flute Concerto 2.  The tempos are lively as the flute plays lilting lead lines.  The Frequency Orchestra once again does this great composer justice through their precise and expressive performance of Mozart's Flute Concerto 2.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Eine Kleine Nachtmusik
volumes.desc: Eine Kleine Nachtmusik (A Little Night Music) is perhaps the most famous and well-loved composition by Wolgang Amadeus Mozart.  Arranged for spare strings, the piece is full of driving rhythms, regal melodies and dramatic dynamic shifts.  The Frequency Orchestra performs Eine Kleine Nachtmusik with the energy and passion that it deserves.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Selections From The Magic Flute
volumes.desc: These selections from Mozart's The Magic Flute include some of the most well-known pieces of Classical operatic music.  The orchestra is in full power throughout and the vocals are dramatic and expressive.  The famous "Queen of The Night Aria" features one of the greatest, and most difficult, vocal lines in all of Classical music, and the Overture shows the height of Mozart's compositional skills.  The Frequency Orchestra skillfully executes these classic selections from Mozart's The Magic Flute, displaying the beauty and power of operatic music.

volumes.title: Modern Rock Vol 2
volumes.desc: Modern Rock Vol 2 is Mark Cook's debut collection and it does not disappoint.  This collection covers all the bases; there are laid-back grooves, funky guitars, atmospheric synth and even some sexy vocals.  With some tracks that are moody and mechanical and some that are soaring and organic, Mark Cook's Modern Rock Vol 2 will suit the purposes of many varied projects.

volumes.title: Digital Dreaming Vol 2
volumes.desc: This engaging collection of chilled out electronic grooves from new composer Mark Cook features atmospheric synth, crunchy electric piano and some atmospheric vocals.  Ethereal moods are evoked by the laid-back beats and subtle palpitating bass lines as warm synth swirls through the tracks.  Digital Dreaming Vol 2 is sure to lend a thoughtful and reflective atmosphere to your project.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 3
volumes.desc: Hip Hop Fused Vol 3, the debut from new composer Jovian, is here.  This exciting collection of tracks is filled with stuttering beats, simmering synth and dark bass grooves.  There are exotic guitars, sweeping strings and ethereal vocal samples throughout, making these tracks far more than just your average beats.  Jovian's Hip Hop Fused Vol 3 will supply you with thoughtful and unique grooves.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 4
volumes.desc: These throbbing, atmospheric grooves from composer Jovian are dynamic and varied, making Hip Hop Fused Vol 4 an excellent collection of exciting beats.  With driving drums, sexy guitars and sweeping synth, Jovian's Hip Hop Fused Vol 4 is a dazzling collection of smooth and intense beats that will give dynamic rhythmic texture to your project.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 5
volumes.desc: Composer Jovian's third outing, Hip Hop Fused Vol 5, is full of big beats and laid-back grooves.  With tracks ranging from quietly atmospheric to intensely driving, there is no shortage of variety in this collection.  Hip Hop Fused Vol 5 offers a wealth of varied beats that can make you get up and dance, or lay back and chill, and will compliment almost any project.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 6
volumes.desc: Here is another collection of booming beats from Jovian: Hip Hop Fused Vol 6.  Exotic string samples, moody synth, funky guitars and driving drums power these tracks that are equally suited for the club or the living room.  Jovian's Hip Hop Fused Vol 6 is a dynamic collection of tracks that have grooves to fit your mood.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 7
volumes.desc:
Hip Hop Fused Vol 7 is an engaging collection of varied beats, ranging from smooth and subtle to intense and booming.  Composer Jovian mixes funky guitars  
DJ Mar N Dean are back with a volume of varied electronic music that ranges from the sweetly melodic to the darkly ambient.  Eclectic synth work and a wide range of tonal colors perfectly compliment the persistent beats.  Electronic Fused Vol 2 offers moody and atmospheric music that lends itself perfectly to a variety of projects.

volumes.title: Hip Hop Fused Vol 8
volumes.desc: Yet another collection of stunning beats from Jovian, Hip Hop Fused Vol 8 features infectious and dynamic grooves.  Reflective guitars weave their way through booming beats as synthesizers soar throughout this collection of varied tracks.  Hip Hop Fused Vol 8 has plenty of grooves to choose from and all are equally well suited for vastly varying projects.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Debussy Prelude to the Afternoon of a Faun
volumes.desc: Claude Debussy's Prelude to the Afternoon of a Faun is a dramatic and emotive piece that features lush orchestration and dense harmonic motion.  Debussy makes full use of rich seventh chords as the piece slowly drifts conjuring up mystical pastoral images.  The Frequency Orchestra's recording of Debussy's Prelude to the Afternoon of a Faun is a prime example of Romantic composition from one of the masters of the craft and is as graceful as it is dramatic.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Symphony 29
volumes.desc: This light and playful symphony from Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart is full of fluttering strings and graceful melodies.  The piece is upbeat and driving while maintaining a peaceful mood as the beautiful melodies unfold.  The Frequency Orchestra's rendition of Mozart's Symphony 29 is a faithful and dynamic performance of a masterful Classical c

volumes.title: Modern Pop and Lyric Vol 3
volumes.desc: Modern Pop and Lyric Vol 3 is the latest collection from veteran composer Steve Glotzer (Modern Pop and Lyric Vol 1 and 2).  The tracks are warm and intimate while maintaining a mellow atmosphere throughout.  Composer Steve Glotzer's outstanding lead guitar is featured throughout, along with solid, yet subtle, backing from a spare rhythm section.  Modern Pop and Lyric Vol 3 is here to provide the laid-back atmosphere for your project.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Symphony 35
volumes.desc: Another selection from one of the greatest composers in Classical music, Mozart's Symphony 35 is an exciting and dynamic piece.  The tempos are on the lively side throughout as joyful melodies bounce out from the strings.  The Frequency Orchestra does not disappoint with their fresh and dramatic performance of Mozart's Symphony 35.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Symphony 40
volumes.desc: Mozart's 40th Symphony is one of the composer's most enduring and dramatic pieces.  With quick tempos, frantic strings and dense harmonies this piece is engaging and exciting throughout.  The Frequency Orchestra's excellent performance of Mozart's Symphony 40 gives this popular piece new life.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Symphony 41
volumes.desc: This powerful symphony is a study in contrast and tension.  The orchestra is alternately triumphant and subdued as Mozart's compositional skills go on display in his 41st Symphony.  The Frequency Orchestra renders Mozart's Symphony 41 as faithfully and skillfully as required for the work of such a monumental composer.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Selections
volumes.desc: A variety of choice picks from various works of Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart show the versatility and timeless talent of the composer.  The pieces range from the rich and slow choral harmonies of "Ave Verum Corpus" to the quick and intense piano of the famous "Turkish March."  The Frequency Orchestra presents accurate and passionate renditions of these classic selections from Mozart.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Requiem Mass
volumes.desc: Mozart's final work, and perhaps his most powerful, the Requiem Mass features a full orchestra along with a choir and vocal soloists.  The piece is at times intense and foreboding, but also graceful and uplifting in sections.  One can almost see Mozart fighting off the angry hand of death as one listens to the Frequency Orchestra's performance of the Requiem Mass.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Schubert Piano Trio
volumes.desc: This dynamic piano trio by Franz Schubert is full of excitement and drama.  The piano is accompanied by violin and cello and the three instruments work together to bring life to Schubert's radical melodic and harmonic ideas.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Schubert's Piano Trio is as intense and dramatic as it is graceful and subtle.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Verdi Selections
volumes.desc: Giuseppe Verdi was most famous for his operatic works and these three selections from three different operas offer a taste of Verdi's compositional skill.  The vocal sections are muscular and the orchestral accompaniment is equally powerful.  The Frequency Orchestra gives accurate dynamic readings of these selections from Verdi.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mozart Selections From Figaro and Don Giovanni
volumes.desc: Some of Mozart's most enduring works are his operas and two of his greatest operatic compositions, Don Giovanni and The Marriage of Figaro, are explored here through choice selections.  The vocal soloists in these selections show Mozart's talent in writing for the human voice while the orchestra simultaneously reveals the harmonic power of Mozart's compositions.  The Frequency Orchestra's Selections From The Marriage of Figaro and Don Giovanni display Mozart's mastery of the opera form.

volumes.title: Funk Grooves Vol 1
volumes.desc: Funk Grooves Vol 1 is the debut release from new composer Gregory Bennett and his collection of laid-back, grooving tunes is filled with slinking bass lines, driving drums, and funky guitars.  These tracks groove along steadily as the beats unfold, revealing layers of funky goodness.  Funk Grooves Vol 1 will provide the laid-back and funky mood that your project needs.

volumes.title: Evil Intentions Vol 1
volumes.desc: This collection of ambient music is filled with creepy synth and clattering percussion, creating a dark and ominous mood.  Ambient noise gives supernatural life as icy synth stabs in the dark and skittering piano darts around.  Evil Intentions Vol 1 provides a dark and menacing atmosphere.

volumes.title: Evil Intentions Vol 2
volumes.desc: Mystery and tension flow out of these orchestral tracks as images of espionage and dark dealings are evoked.  The orchestra lurks in the shadows as percussion clangs away.  Evil Intentions Vol 2 is the perfect accompaniment to any sort of clandestine activity.

volumes.title: Electronic Fused Vol 3
volumes.desc:
DJ Mar And Dean serve up another absorbing and sonic set of fused tracks with 
Electronic Fused Vol 3, Intense sounds and great use of the stereo field are key features of Mar And Dean's work, this volume of atmospheric tracks does not disappoint! dig the chaotic sounds of "Infiltrates The Darkness", riding a determined drill and bass beat, the scorching synths weave mind-bending lines.
"Electric Fusion" builds a hypnotic melody with wicked synths and a clipped vocal sample as a subtle and spooky chill-out rhythm percolates underneath.
Fresh, engaging and flowing with subtle hooks, Electronic Fused Vol 3 will add distinctive dynamics to your project with it's fresh electronic styles.

volumes.title: TV Themes Vol 3
volumes.desc: This collection of tracks is extremely varied and very catchy with diverse feels and genres being explored throughout.  The tracks run the gamut of musical styles, from Dub Reggae and slick Pop to Bossa Nova and Smooth Jazz.  TV Themes Vol 3 offers a wide range of tracks that will fit perfectly in an equally wide range of projects.

volumes.title: Fairytales Vol 1
volumes.desc: Mystical themes abound throughout this collection of orchestral tracks as images of mysterious forests and magical kingdoms are effectively evoked by the orchestra.  Fairytales Vol 1 sets a scene of fantasy and wonder that will enhance a variety of projects.

volumes.title: Drama Vol 3
volumes.desc: Epic strings, strong horns and driving percussion are featured throughout this compelling collection of orchestral tracks.  Tension and mystery abound as the orchestra conjures up images of narrow escapes and secret dealings.  Drama Vol 3 is the perfect match for the action and espionage in your project.

volumes.title: Celtic Themes Vol 1
volumes.desc: Images of the Emerald Isle emerge gracefully in this collection as flute and harp take center stage amidst lush orchestral accompaniment.  Poignant melodies drift softly like mist over the moors with subtle percussion acting to accent the reflective orchestration.  Celtic Themes Vol 1 will provide a thoughtful and mystical atmosphere for your project.

volumes.title: Battle Themes Vol 2
volumes.desc: These orchestral tracks are full of epic intensity as strings and horns surge forward powerfully.  Soldierly rhythms drive these tracks as scenes of warfare are brought to life through music.  Battle Themes Vol 2 is the perfect backdrop for any epic struggle.

volumes.title: Mystical Symphonic Vol 3
volumes.desc: Lush orchestration is featured throughout this collection of sweepingly powerful tracks.  A cinematic feel is created through perfect use of lush harmonies and reflective melodies as strings, horns and woodwinds work in perfect harmony.  Mystical Symphonic Vol 3 provides a beautiful musical setting for a variety of projects.

volumes.title: Medieval Symphonic Vol 1
volumes.desc: This collection of period music features plaintive harp, subtle percussion and effective orchestral arrangements.  Images of olden times abound through the choice of instrumentation and the melodic tendencies of the tracks.  Medieval Symphonic Vol 1 is appropriate accompaniment to period-piece projects.

volumes.title: Epic Themes Vol 1
volumes.desc: Tension and drama fill these orchestral tracks.  Frantic strings, muscular horns and intense vocals bring a furious feel to the tracks as images of epic battles and narrow escapes are evoked.  Epic Themes Vol 1 will bring tension and drama to legendary tales.

volumes.title: World Holiday Vol 1
volumes.desc: In this bright and happy collection familiar holiday songs are given an island vacation.  Funky guitars and loping rhythms set the stage for sparkling marimbas as a variety of different takes on traditional Christmas songs are explored.  It's never the wrong time of year for the holiday spirit, especially when the tracks are as warm and sunny as on World Holiday Vol 1.

volumes.title: Action and Adventure Vol 3
volumes.desc: These orchestral tracks are filled with sweeping strings and pounding percussion as epic moods emerge.  Scenes ointrospective grace. The diverse emotional tastes of this album are staggering and sure to captivate audiences. Be sure to tune into Jared Jones' "Impress Ya," now on Freeplay Indie!

volumes.title: TV Themes Vol 4
volumes.desc: A funky groove persists throughout this collection of catchy tunes.  Wah-wah guitars, punchy horns and soulful organ fill the space as jazz-inflected electric guitar leads light the way.  TV Themes Vol 4 will provide a funky and upbeat groove without fail.

volumes.title: Action and Adventure Vol 4
volumes.desc: Picture yourself on the high seas as these orchestral tracks surge forward tumultuously like waves on the deck of a pirate ship.  Furious strings and ominous horns act to build tension throughout this collection of action-packed tracks.  Action and Adventure Vol 4 will have you hoisting the Jolly Roger in no time, so be sure to include this volume in your project or else you'll be forced to walk the plank!

volumes.title: Sports Extreme Vol 4
volumes.desc: This collection of hard rocking tracks is as varied as it is exciting.  Everything from crunchy guitar pop to heavy, techno-inflected rock is explored here as an energetic feel is maintained throughout.  Sports Extreme Vol 4 is as suitable for everything from Nascar to BMX racing, and will surely add excitement to your project.

volumes.title: Medieval Symphonic Vol 2
volumes.desc: These orchestral tracks conjure images of isolated fiefdoms and towering castles  as the Middle Ages are brought to life.  You can almost see the serfs tilling the fields as mystical melodies emerge from strings and flutes, with lush orchestral accompaniment creating a vibrant atmosphere of olden times.  Medieval Symphonic Vol 2 sets the stage for period pieces perfectly.

volumes.title: Kids Songs Vol 2
volumes.desc:
Composer David Flavin's new set, "Kids Songs Vol 2" is a delightful romping joy-ride, featuring tooting horns, clowning congas and hurdy-gurdy organs a-plenty. 
Bring the fun with tracks like "Zoo Visitor" and "Games Are Fun" then give 'em a break with the charming "Sleepy Time" lullaby. Excellent production and imaginative orchestration brings these tracks alive with smiles and joy.
Kids Songs Vol 2 gives you picture perfect tracks sure to tickle your funny bone.

volumes.title: Tech Grooves Vol 6
volumes.desc: Breezy beats and atmospheric synths are features heavily in this set of electronic tracks.  These tracks are as suitable for the club as they are for a quiet highway as a cool and carefree feel persists throughout.  Tech Grooves Vol 6 is mood music that creates the perfect atmosphere.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Mussorgsky Pictures At An Exhibition
volumes.desc: A solo piano piece, Pictures At An Exhibition paints a vivid picture through rich harmonic textures and a reflective melody.  Mussorgsky's Pictures At An Exhibition is as graceful as it is thought-provoking and the Frequency Orchestra plays the piece with emotion and accuracy.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Offenbach Selections
volumes.desc: The work of French Romantic composer Jacques Offenbach is given a brief overview here as two of his most well-known pieces are displayed.  The Barcarole from his opera, the Tales of Hoffman, is graceful and harmonically rich and the famous Can Can from Orpheus in the Underworld is forceful and playful simultaneously.  The Frequency Orchestra does justice to these two classic works by Offenbach.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Pachelbel Canon in D
volumes.desc: One of the most famous pieces of Classical music, Johann Pachelbel's Canon in D has truly stood the test of time and is as powerful today as it was more than three hundred years ago.  The Frequency Orchestra performs the Canon in D with poise and power, with a large range of tonal colors to convey the emotion of this timeless piece.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Paganini Violin Concerto 4
volumes.desc: Niccolo Paganini was one of the most admired and revered violinists of his time and his fourth Violin Concerto shows why.  The full range of the violin's musical potential is used in this piece and the skill necessary to execute some of the dramatic passages is immense.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Paganini's Violin Concerto 4 is beautifully executed, with special commendation for the fleet-fingered violinist.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Parry Jerusalem
volumes.desc: This choral piece by English composer Hubert Parry utilizes a poem by William Blake for its lyrics.  The orchestra and choir combine their powers to lift this piece to the heavens as it builds steadily to a triumphant conclusion.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Parry's Jerusalem is dramatic and exultant.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Pergolesi Stabat Mater
volumes.desc: Giovanni Battista Pergolesi's musical setting for Stabat Mater is a dramatic and doleful piece.  Stately Baroque harmonies move the piece forward as plaintive vocals weave around each other, creating dense movement.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Pergolesi's Stabat Mater is a beautiful example of Baroque sacred music.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Ponchielli Dance Of The Hours
volumes.desc: The great operatic composer Amilcare Ponchielli is probably best known for this work, The Dance Of The Hours, from his most famous opera, La Gioconda.  Gently dancing strings carry the piece forward with a playful melody that unfolds subtly as the orchestra builds.  The Frequency Orchestra plays Ponchielli's Dance of The Hours with careful attention to harmonic and rhythmic detail and the piece unfolds beautifully.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Puccini Selections
volumes.desc: Giacomo Puccini composed some of the greatest operatic works of all time and these selections from his most famous operas display the power of Puccini's work.  The focus is on the vocalist in these tracks as the orchestra mimics the emotional arc of the vocals.  The selection from the famous Turandot is the highlight here with epic vocals that lift the music up to unbelievable heights of emotional power.  The Frequency Orchestra plays these pieces with passion and power, doing justice to some of Puccini's greatest works.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Purcell Selections
volumes.desc: English Baroque composer Henry Purcell was one of the most talented artists of his time.  These selections give a brief glimpse into perhaps the greatest musical mind of the 17th century.  The Frequency Orchestra gives these selections period-appropriate treatments that allow for the details of composition to emerge.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Respighi Ancient Airs And Dances Suite
volumes.desc: Ottorino Respighi was as much a musicologist as he was a composer and this suite  displays his interest in pre-Classical music.  The melodies are appropriately  antiquated as Respighi explores the modal styles of the 16th and 17th centuries.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Respighi's Ancient Airs And Dances Suite is captivating and dramatic.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Respighi Fountains of Rome
volumes.desc: Respighi's most famous work, and part of the Roman Trilogy, Fountains of Rome paints vivid pictures with dense and colorful orchestral figures.  Strings and horns work together as the melodies cascade dramatically.  The Frequency Orchestra brings Rome to life with their performance of Respighi's Fountains of Rome.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Respighi Pines of Rome
volumes.desc: The Frequency Orchestra is in full force for Respighi's Pines of Rome, a piece that bursts with life.  Part of the Roman Trilogy, Respighi's Pines of Rome is a study in dynamics.  The pieces dramatically turn from almost silent to triumphantly loud, lifting the music to dramatic heights.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Respighi Roman Festivals
volumes.desc: This intense and drama

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Respighi The Birds Suite
volumes.desc: Respighi's knowledge of past musical styles is evident in The Birds Suite. Pieces from the 18th century are given a new treatment, but in a traditional style, as bird songs are mimicked by the orchestra.  Each section of the piece after the Prelude is devoted to a different bird: hen, dove, nightingale and cuckoo, respectively.  The Frequency Orchestra uses subtle power to drive Respighi's The Birds Suite as the piece unfolds beautifully.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Rimsky Korsakov Flight Of The Bumble Bee
volumes.desc: Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov was one of the great Russian composers of the 19th century and Flight Of The Bumble Bee

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Rossini Selections
volumes.desc: This overview of the work of Gioachino Rossini includes some of his most famous pieces.  The Barber of Seville and the William Tell Overture are two of the most recognizable pieces of Classical music, and both had significant impact on later composers, as well as on contemporary popular culture.  A strong sense of dynamic tension drives Rossini's work and makes these pieces captivating and dramatic.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of these selections by Rossini does not disappoint and offers time-tested tunes played with power.

The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Schubert's Piano Trio in B Flat is a classic work from one of history's most highly regarded composers.

Frequency Orch. Sarasate Selections
volumes.desc: Spanish Romantic composer Pablo Sarasate was also an extremely accomplished violinist and these selections allow for serious tests of the limits of the instrument.  The famous Carmen Fantasy utilizes an orchestral backdrop to support impressively fast and expressive violin work with more than a touch of Spanish flavor.  Sarasate's Zapateado features piano and violin, with the violin doing things that should be impossible.  Special credit is deserved for the Frequency Orchestra's violinist on these selections from the works of Sarasate.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Satie Gymnopodie 1
volumes.desc: Erik Satie was at the forefront of French avant-garde music for much of his professional career and his famous Gymnopodies were some of his earliest masterpieces.  Gymnopodie 1 is a heavily atmospheric piece that relies more on mood than on traditional Western harmonic values.  A simple melody glides over lush chordal accompaniment in a wistful manner, creating a deeply introspective atmosphere.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Schubert Piano Trio in B Flat
volumes.desc: This wonderful piece features piano, violin and cello in a joyful and triumphant manner.  The strong rhythmic drive of the piece makes the graceful playing that much more effective as the strings soar confidently above the sparkling piano work.  The Frequency Orchestra's performance of Schubert's Piano Trio in B Flat is a classic work from one of history's most highly regarded composers.

volumes.title: Frequency Orch. Schubert Selections
volumes.desc: These selections from the work of Franz Schubert exhibit the composer's considerable skill and passion for religious vocal music.  The famous Ave Maria is uplifting and bittersweet with just sparse piano to accompany the beautiful vocals.  The Gloria, Kyrie and Salve Regina all feature a full choir that lends an appropriately triumphant atmosphere to the lyrical subject matter.  These selections by Schubert, as performed by the Frequency Orchestra, are powerful pieces of timeless music.

volumes.title: Electronic Fused Vol 4
volumes.desc:
DJ's Mar and Dean newest release, Electronic Fused Vol 4, is a potent mix of slamming, glitched beats and amazing, atmospheric synth work. Dig the ethereal synths and quirky rhythms of "Eternal Effervescence"- otherworldly synths weave a fluid ambiance as a funky kick works a stop-start beat.
"Wayward Struggle" features a synth that sounds like electric ocean waves, as a glitched kick comes in insane synths come alive with all sorts of beeps and buzzes for an exciting and mesmerizing track. The excellent production allows the fresh synth sounds to shine, the otherworldly melodies to sparkle and the beats to punch right through. Electronic Fused Vol 4 is a fantastic set of tracks that will bring a danceable tech edge to any project or scene.

volumes.title: Ambient Figures Vol 3
volumes.desc:
New composer Ezekiel Honig brings a new slant on ambient music with Ambient Figures Vol 3, utilizing found sounds to weave organic, earthy, background rhythms he brings a new edge to the normal ambient calmness. Simple rhodes organ chords are manipulated to give a resonant, echoing feel that gives these tracks a human touch. "Moments Of Materiality" features a quirky lo-fi rhythm and ringing keys to weave an upbeat melody that flows with a child-like happiness. "Green And Metal Thumbs's" echoing rhodes and clockwork percussion meld into a lo-fi groove, moving with an organic pace, with it's simple chords weaving an otherworldly tune. Ambi
