tracks.title: Bach Brandenburg Concerto 4 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Shimmering solos and energetic melodies tie up the 3rd movement, it's eager rhythms pushing the emotive theme.

tracks.title: Bach Brandenburg Concerto 5 (1st movement)

tracks.title: Bach Brandenburg Concerto 5 (2nd movement)

tracks.title: Bach Brandenburg Concerto 5 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: This engaging melody has a country air, filled with freshness and color, a feast for the ears.

tracks.title: Dvorak New World Symphony (4th movement)

tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Deserted Ship
tracks.desc: Echoing choral voices, sound effects and bells create an excellently representational aural feeling of an abandoned ship floating aimlessly at sea. Hulking and empty.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Difficult To Breathe
tracks.desc: Eerie, obstinate bell melody builds a tense atmosphere, strings and percussion add dynamic, suspenseful accents.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: The Expedition
tracks.desc: A stalwart, serious piece with orchestral elements colliding into a driving military beat, the falling melody speaks of trials and tribulations.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Fading Desire
tracks.desc: Forlorn piano line wanders into percussion effects and sad strings, synth effects weave a dark, moody atmosphere.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Remain Hidden
tracks.desc: Dark synth percussion effects weave a moody rhythm for a spooky, meandering harpsichord, strings sing with an evil glint, forlorn and ominous.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Underground Resevior
tracks.desc: Downcast piano weaves a dramatic melody, tense strings and cymbal effects add atmosphere as a single bell spells out the blue melody, strings join with mourning lines that try to lift the abysmal melody but fail as the turgid piano returns.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Dark Side Of The Groove
tracks.desc: A mechanical snare weaves a clockwork beat, percolating synth arpeggios build a motivational underbelly for a poppy accordion melody. Syncopated synths add catchy accents.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Dark Soundscape
tracks.desc: A quirky arpeggio bubbles and chimes as waves of synth pad float across the top, a beat comes in with lighthearted push and a flowing bass figure, synths add an expansive atmosphere as the beat works underneath.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Darkness Prevails
tracks.desc: Crazy synth sounds weave a smooth electronic beat, a flute-like synth add soulful accents, a quirky laid-back groove with neat syncopated synth elements, ear-chatching and fun.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Digital Imprint
tracks.desc: Boxy synths and a driving dance beat weave a tight groove, the break kicks in with flowing clouds of synth, the cool groove kicks back in.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Driving In The Dark
tracks.desc: Dark pads and synth effects float over a dense electronic beat, flashing synths and gurgling pads weave a moody atmosphere as the shadowy rhythm bubbles.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Electric Attack
tracks.desc: A driving house beat kicks with a robotic grind. Wacked out synths add a dark, syncopated effects. Spooky, pushing and strangely catchy.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Elliptical Revolution
tracks.desc: Cooly snapping step beat bubbles under moody synth pads, catchy syncopation accents give a pop asthetic to the strange sounds gliding around the driving beat.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Industrial Sector
tracks.desc: Strange synths weave a rhythmic atmosphere, a glitchy beat comes in as computer noises add syncopated accents. The beats drop out for a spacey break, then the dark glitchy beat takes over.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Losing My Mind
tracks.desc: Effected synths build an odd melody as a cool hi-hat and snare kick a glitchy beat, odd breaks add ear-grabbing pauses.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Wasted Resources
tracks.desc: Robotic noises bubble underneath a slamming tech beat, hip shaking beats kick with mechanical abandon. Quirky but catchy.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Insistent Rhythm
tracks.desc: Smooth, strolling beat glides under cloud pads with an easy groove, bubbling synth noises add texture and depth.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Mystery Groove
tracks.desc: Mellow groove with a punchy snare, spacy synth pads add an atmospheric sheen. The easy beat is accented by swirling delay effects that add dimension to the slow rhythm.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Point Of No Return
tracks.desc: Boxy, slow beat accented by handclaps, guitar samples lay little riffs as a piano drops a little funk run, string pads and organ add cool melodic effects. A mysterious kyoto enters with a punchy solo.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Sexy Ride
tracks.desc: Bubbly, percolating synths weave a humid atmosphere over an easy stepping funk beat with warm, swelling organ accenting. Groovy breaks add rich dimensions to the funk textures.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Split Open
tracks.desc: Ladi back groove with a 70's feel in the synths, upbeat with a moody edge. The easy glide beat moves effortlessly.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Take Off
tracks.desc: Bubbling effects and bells weave a warped melody for a sneaky street beat, darkly simmering.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: The Way You Groove
tracks.desc: Poppin' step beat with a laid-back feel, atmospheric synths add humid fields, string synths add an edege to the funky break.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: West Side Of Town
tracks.desc: Fat bass and a calm beat weave a slow groove, belled synths add melodic textures, warping effects give the synths cool, modulating echos.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Army Angels
tracks.desc: Booming, millitary horn lines over driving drum machine beats, pulsing synth effects add tension and push to this commanding suspence track.

tracks.title: Cold Kill
tracks.desc: Filtered, percolating rhythms create a tense push, whistling synths add flowing lines, kicking into a fat groove.

tracks.title: Face To Face
tracks.desc: A seriously driving machine beat pushes tense horn lines, a spacey flute interlude gives a breather, then the driving beat kicks back in.

tracks.title: Force Combat
tracks.desc: Bells, oud and flutes weave Mid-Eeastern melodies over a driving, no-nonsense beat.

tracks.title: Ground Squad
tracks.desc: Real orchestral percussion builds a tense rhythm bed with sneaky undertones, Driving horn section weaves a complex, compelling melody.

tracks.title: Maneater
tracks.desc: Spooky intro with flutes and effects, a driving arpeggio kicks in with syncopated synth noises, the rhythm floats and pauses building a tense feel that releases with a pulsing jungle beat.

tracks.title: Peacemaker
tracks.desc: Driving rock beats with distorted guitars weaving a dark, urgent rhtythm, orchestral instruments add pulsing accents, the driving beat carries the melodies with dark determination.

tracks.title: Strike Eagle
tracks.desc: Vibrant, striking horn lines and pulsing arpeggios drive this aggressive track, the drum machine rhythm percolates and pauses, adding to the tense builds.

tracks.title: Tank Battle
tracks.desc: A compelling mix of orchestral and world flavors weave a tense atmosphere, millitary drums come in with an urgent push and fade, between the flues and synths build tense humid soundscapes.

tracks.title: Werewolf
tracks.desc: An exotic beat with shakers pulses beneith dark synth effects and driving horn lines.

tracks.title: City Landfill
tracks.desc: This atmospheric piece begins with tense strings and acoustic guitar weaving a hazy glow, a drum machine featuring millitary snares comes in with a dramatic pulse and fades leaving the tense strings, dark horns and bassy piano hits floating in the air.

tracks.title: Cool Town
tracks.desc: Piano and guitar build a sad, moody melody, synth drums weave a dark stop/start pulse. Strings add taut counterpoint.

tracks.title: Keep Cool
tracks.desc: Dark, throbbing bass lines and synthetic beats build a dark rhythm for atmospheric synth pads and echoing guitars, the track builds as horns and strings add dramatic accents, but always keeps a razor edege and never explodes.

tracks.title: Massive Assault
tracks.desc: Strings and echoing piano weave a dark, dank atmosphere, horns lend a snaking melody, a effected synth beat brings a halting rhythm. The lost, downbeat melody speaks of darker days and trying times.

tracks.title: Minor Rock
tracks.desc: Minor piano keys add a spark of daylight to this turgid track, percolating arpeggio synths add a dark bed, horns and synth pads weave a stern melody as percussion adds dynamic impacts.

tracks.title: On The Run
tracks.desc: Echoing flute and exotic percussion give a world feel to this picturesque piece, edgy, rushing horn lines and rolling kettle drums bring a tense push with dramatic flourshes.

tracks.title: Temptation Place
tracks.desc: Sneaky orchestral percussion elements weave a hide and seek rhythm, emotive horn hits, synth bells and snaking electric guitar add dynamic pulsing accents. With an undercover spy feel.

tracks.title: The Alarm
tracks.desc: A punchy, live drum beat simmers under a thundering horn melody, synth effects add syncopated accents.

tracks.title: Under
tracks.desc: Echoing, effected drums build a heartbeat rhythm, eerie synth fade and grow like shadows, a filtered beat comes in and an echoing piano adds a far away melody.

tracks.title: Glinka Russlan and Ludmilla (Overture)
tracks.desc: This bounding, lighthearted overture features lovely cello lines and a bright graceful spirit.

tracks.title: Grieg Holberg Suite (Air)
tracks.desc: Sweeping, striding strings weave a poignant melody, open and meditative, welcoming joy, and welcoming sorrow.

tracks.title: Grieg Holberg Suite (Gavotte Minuet)
tracks.desc: This charming piece for strings has a regal air and a lighthearted step, the dancing sprightly chorus has an earnest pulse.

tracks.title: Grieg Holberg Suite (Prelude)
tracks.desc: This rousing motivational piece sings with unbounded joy. A sunny heartwarming melody builds and cascades with love.

tracks.title: Grieg Holberg Suite (Rigaudon)
tracks.desc: Trilling strings open with a folky, fast paced melody, slowing into a darker meditation and leaping back to life with dancing joy.

tracks.title: Grieg Holberg Suite (Sarabande)
tracks.desc: Lilting, warm strings weave an elegant melody, growing and gliding with a peaceful kindness.

tracks.title: Grieg In The Hall Of The Mountain King (from the Peer Gynt Suite)
tracks.desc: This memorable, industrious melody begins slowly and builds to a thundering momentous climax.

tracks.title: Grieg March Of The Trolls
tracks.desc: This vivid piece struts with energy and an animalistic curiosity, it's gentle moments have a delighted air of wonder, while it's excited moments flash with passion.

tracks.title: Grieg Morning Mood (from the Peer Gynt Suite)
tracks.desc: This charming and ethereal melody warms the heart with is shining, untarnished glide. Growing with a peaceful grace and grandeur.

tracks.title: Grieg Piano Concerto 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: The resounding, opening leads to a striking, emotive passage with hints of Norwegan folk melodies and flowing, shifting moods and feelings.

tracks.title: Grieg Piano Concerto 1 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Regal and knowing, the lilting intro is lead by flowing strings and reassured, twinkling piano lines, Dramatic in it's ease and grace, this reflective piece dances with the light of love.

tracks.title: Grieg Piano Concerto 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Engaging piano lines are answered by an energetic orchestra throughout this warm, emotive movement, the heady romantic melodies peak with epic swells and ebb with elegant, reflective grace.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Agnus Dei)
tracks.desc: A captivating and gentile chorus leads this loving requiem, reassuring and comforting melodies move with a spiritual air.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (In Paradisum)
tracks.desc: Warm, melodic organ lines weave a delicate and embracing tune as a rich mixed vocal chorus sings sweetly of redemption and peace.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Introit and Kyrie)
tracks.desc: Dark, strident orchestra paints bold strokes as a rich chorus develops a somber, earnest polyphony.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Libera Me)
tracks.desc: Thrumming strings weave deep rhythms in this mystical track, a proud solo voice sings for mercy, the chorus and orchestra foreshadow calamity and judgement.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Offertory)
tracks.desc: This contemplative piece features rising, mystical chanting and an opulent backing of strings and organ, the theme speaks of kind reminiscence and hope.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Pie Jesu)
tracks.desc: This restful piece features enveloping orchestral lines and a sweetly soloing voice rising like the sun from the humid melodies, singing of peace and acceptance.

tracks.title: Faure Requiem (Sanctus)
tracks.desc: This magical mass slowly builds to epic, swirling heights, with warm harp, strings and organ swelling in spiritual joy. Powerful and climatic chorus resounds with inspired rapture.

tracks.title: Faure Barcarolle 1 from Opus 20
tracks.desc: Calm and measured solo piano slowly weaves a tender and reflective melody, building in the middle section with a questioning tone, becoming accepting, perhaps resigned, but with an underlying positive feel.

tracks.title: Faure Berceuse Opus 16
tracks.desc: This piece, the first version for piano and violin alone, floats with an attentive, knowing air. The fine violin lines slowly caress the gentile piano accompaniment.

tracks.title: Faure Pavane For Orchestra Opus 50
tracks.desc: There is a mysterious air in the plucked strings and sweet choral voices in this ethereal track, moving gently with an earthy, natural flow.

tracks.title: Faure Pelleas and Melisande (Sicilienne)
tracks.desc: This harmonically rich incidental piece moves with refined luxuriousness, flute and strings swaying lithely like a warm breeze.

tracks.title: Handel Organ Concerto 13 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A reassuring melody with trilling organ and sparkling bells has a cheery holiday flavor in it's warm refrain.

tracks.title: Handel Organ Concerto 13 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Dancing strings and organ weave a delighted, mystical emotion. Eager call and response flourishes resound with joy and commanding purpose.

tracks.title: Handel Organ Concerto 13 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Resounding organ lines weave a emotional melody, with a mystical and enraptured vibe.

tracks.title: Handel Organ Concerto 13 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Organ, strings and harpsichord weave a introspective melody with an elegant pace, radiating with a calm and peaceful light.

tracks.title: Handel Organ Concerto 13 (5th movement)
tracks.desc: Ringing strings and propulsive organ weave a delightful, joyous melody, ever pushing forward with a gleaming courage.

tracks.title: Handel And He Shall Purify (from the Messiah)
tracks.desc: A full chorus rigs gloriously in this exalting piece. The orchestra reaches skyward in it's glowing accompaniment.

tracks.title: Handel And The Glory Of The Lord (from the Messiah)
tracks.desc: Exalting voices joyously echo above a gently dancing orchestra.

tracks.title: Handel Behold The Lamb Of God (from the Messiah)
tracks.desc: This warm and emotive piece shimmers with a heavenly light. Graceful voices mingle wnd shine.

tracks.title: Handel For Unto Us A Child Is Born (from the Messiah)
tracks.desc: This celebratory melody shines with hope and love, the chorus simmers with a giddy, proud spirit.

tracks.title: Handel Halleluliah Chorus (from the Messiah)
tracks.desc: This beloved chorus sings praises to the high heavens with exuberant exaltation. Dynamic, worldly and invigorating.

tracks.title: Handel I Know My Redeemer Liveth (Messiah)
tracks.desc: This slow, introspective piece has a gentle sway, the engaging instruments echoing the vocals glorious melody.

tracks.title: Handel Harp Concerto (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Elegant, sinuous harp weaves a gentle melody, sparkling and kind. The orchestra add rhythmic flourishes and decoration.

tracks.title: Handel Harp Concerto (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: A gently lilting piece with strings adding rising lines to the sparking harp.

tracks.title: Handel Harp Concerto (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: A jaunty tune with charming harp lines, twisting and merging with the gentle orchestra.

tracks.title: Handel Air 1 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: Regal strings swell with a shining pride, beating a subtle rhythm the melody floats with assured poise.

tracks.title: Handel Air 2 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: Dancing baroque strings sing of kingly adventure and royal escapades, with a cheeky, upbeat gleam the melody preens and swoons.

tracks.title: Handel Allegro 1 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: Gracious horns weave a towering introduction, with a regal beat and open, welcoming arms.

tracks.title: Handel Allegro 2 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: The orchestra rings out an announcement of courage and splendor with a joyous excitement.

tracks.title: Handel Allegro Molto (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This curious piece is lead by oboe and bassoon giving it an odd earthy quality, encouraging and playful ornamentation gives this busy piece charm.

tracks.title: Handel Allegro Vigoroso (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This galloping track has a folky, familial emotion, the splendid flute solo is merry and jovial as the orchestra answers in an excited call and response.

tracks.title: Handel Andante Con Moto (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This downbeat piece sings with a lonesome, crestfallen voice, heart-crushed flourishes weave a delicate tale of sorrow.

tracks.title: Handel Bourree (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This short movement pulses with vigor and energy, a heroic theme.

tracks.title: Handel Bourree and Hornpipe 1 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This piece builds from the Bourree and takes the melody on a swooning dance with both charm and strength.

tracks.title: Handel Hornpipe 1 (from the Water Music Suite)
tracks.desc: This whirling intro moves with a jaunty pace, blooming forth like a invigorating spring day.

tracks.title: Handel Arrival Of The Queen Of Sheba
tracks.desc: Often used for the entrance of the bride in wedding ceremonies, this delightful, exuberant track is welcoming and warm. Shining and emotive rhythms gently pulse with light.

tracks.title: Handel Concerto Grosso 6
tracks.desc: Upbeat rhythms push this warm, sweeping concerto. Kaleidoscopic melodies intertwine in lovely ways, a magical polyphony.

tracks.title: Handel Dank Sei Dir Herr
tracks.desc: This sweet and lilting piece spills over with kind love, a majestic string melody accompanies a melancholic mixed chorus with a sweeping, gentle flow.

tracks.title: Handel Jephtha Waft Her Angels
tracks.desc: This patient oratorio for solo voice breathes with light and lament, lovely and sad. A calm lilting rhythm with a processional feel.

tracks.title: Handel Judas Maccabeus
tracks.desc: This epic oratorio moves with a proud refrain, war drums beat as the heroic horns peal, celebrating a hard won victory.

tracks.title: Handel La Rejouissance (from the Royal Fireworks Music)
tracks.desc: This explosive and colorful piece beats with a celebratory pomp and shine. The warm, rushing horns sing of action and adventure ahead.

tracks.title: Handel Largo (from Xerxes)
tracks.desc: Flowing strings paint gossamer melodies brimming with light, sweetly swooning and full of promise.

tracks.title: Handel Minuet (from Berenice)
tracks.desc: This charmed piece steps with a gentle rhythm, flowing in a mystical reverie, as the elegant string lines weave a heartwarming melody.

tracks.title: Handel Overture (from Julius Caesar)
tracks.desc: Robust and resounding strings intro this dynamic track. The horn section joins and the winding melodies surge with a joyous imprudence.

tracks.title: Handel Sarabande (from Suite 11 in D minor)
tracks.desc: This baroque dance for harpsichord moves with a victorian grace, gently and reverently played. A mystic and timeless spirit pervades this singular air.

tracks.title: Babylon
tracks.desc: An odd, short piece: horns and chorus build to a forceful peak and fade, after a silence, the piece winds down with sparkling accents.

tracks.title: Barbarian
tracks.desc: A darkly simmering track, growling strings weave an eerie melody accented by ghostly flute. Kettle drums and shakers add a skelital rhythm.

tracks.title: Cairo Chase
tracks.desc: Grand horns weave a desert-flavored intro as ethnic instruments jump into a folky, fast-paced jam. The propulsive rhythms burn with an edgy pulse.

tracks.title: Catacombs
tracks.desc: This nervy, tense atmospheric track seeths with a palpable edge, dark bass chorus and cellos weave shadowy melodies, accented by white-knuckle violin plucks and noises.

tracks.title: Free People
tracks.desc: Swelling voice, strings and winds weave into a homogeneous, beautiful sound, rising and warming like the sun, earthy percussion comes in as the piece opens majestically.

tracks.title: Golden Sphinx
tracks.desc: Horns provide a deep, bassy foundation for dark jungle drums and eerie string lines, oud adds a rhythmic line to the winding, omnious track, Throbbing horns signal a resounding call and the sullen rhythms fade.

tracks.title: Horus
tracks.desc: Echoing percussion and winding flutes weave an exotic, mysterious rhythm, tense strings and eerie plucked oud add dynamic accents. Building and fading but burning with dark intentions.

tracks.title: Light Exploration
tracks.desc: Keening strings weave a taut note, flute and harp bring warm melodies as light percussion adds a growing glow. The piece warms and flows into a gentile glide.

tracks.title: The Polis
tracks.desc: Urgent strings and pushing percussion weave a dark dirge, slashing strokes from strings are accented by cymbals, a tense, edge of seat track.

tracks.title: Warriors Arise!
tracks.desc: A dark intro with flutes, female voice and slashing percussion, horns join in as does a dark, demonic chorus to heighten the gloom and doom.

tracks.title: World Wonder
tracks.desc: A throbbing, dark track with moody strings, evil, encroaching cellos and tense plucked harp. Bashing percussion pushes the winding melody with unrelenting urgency.

tracks.title: Crawl And Hide
tracks.desc: A crashing intro fades as taut strings ring, giving an eye of the storm feel. Military drums flex and twitch, like an itchy trigger finger waiting for it's mark.

tracks.title: Empire Air Force
tracks.desc: Koto and Shinobue (flute) add international flavors to this driving military march. Strings peal like sirens and horns give dark warning blasts.

tracks.title: Field Forces
tracks.desc: Urgent string lines and troubled horns weave a life or death melody, marching snares beat a persistant tattoo.

tracks.title: Growing Danger
tracks.desc: Bleating horns and thundering percussion build a driving bed for slashing string and desperate trumpet blasts. With a time-sensitive feel.

tracks.title: Gun Attack
tracks.desc: Snares beat a brutal rhythm with unrelenting push, deep, harsh horn blasts flash, trembling strings weave strident lines. With a time is up feel.

tracks.title: Lost Wars
tracks.desc: Rolling timpani and echoing snares weave a simmering rhythm as a cello growls and slithers, sound effects add an eerie haze to the expectant atmosphere.

tracks.title: Naval Combat
tracks.desc: Echoing flute and cymbal effects weave a humid atmosphere for rapid-fire snares, keening string add a palpable tension. Plucked koto add an international flair to the serious track.

tracks.title: Navy Seals
tracks.desc: Bells and french horn add a twist to the thundering horns and strident, trembling strings, pounding snares keep anxious time.

tracks.title: Objective Combat
tracks.desc: Thundering rhythms lead this apprehensive track, anxious string pulses and searing, bassy horn lines weave a dark melody.

tracks.title: Operation Eagle
tracks.desc: Echoing snare rolls work a marching rhythm as harsh horns weave a turgid, lost melody. Panicked strings keep double time with the relentless snares.

tracks.title: Prevailing Soldier
tracks.desc: Flowing horn lines weave a courageous melody as snares keep a sublime beat. Rising with power and might and ending on a warm note.

tracks.title: Reinforcements
tracks.desc: A slowly evolving undercover feel fills this tense track, the abrupt horn blasts like close calls, seething with the fear of being discovered.

tracks.title: Target Mission
tracks.desc: Spooky bells and growling cellos weave a claustrophobic atmosphere, strings and horns build crashing pulses that ring out with anxious echos, hovering over an abyss.

tracks.title: Bad Sossa
tracks.desc: Melancholy female vocal vamps over a breezy bossa, acoustic and electric guitars provide mellow riffing. Easy rhythms are accented by chiming xylophone.

tracks.title: Full Sun
tracks.desc: Sweet, gliding flue solo and jazzy belled rhodes organ leads this easy strolling bossa, shakers and acoustic guitars provide rhythmic accents to the beachy beats.

tracks.title: Ghost Boss
tracks.desc: Jazzy drumming and upbeat acoustic guitar riffing weave a thoughtful groove. Lounge style synths and electric piano add atmospheric accents.

tracks.title: Mediation
tracks.desc: Lively female vamping leads this sparkling, motivational track. A 12 string acoustic provides a charming solo, strings add a warm glide.

tracks.title: Mediterranean
tracks.desc: Cool, syncopated rim shots give a unique push tho this jazzy bossa, piano and organ weave melodic steps for easy flowing horn solos.

tracks.title: Close To The Evil
tracks.desc: Distorted percussion rings like murky gunshots, groaning, echoing synths weave an oppressive sound. Odd synth effects add impactful accents.

tracks.title: Danger At Hand
tracks.desc: Synth heartbeats and trembling strings fade and swell, growling echo rise from the murky depths.

tracks.title: Dark Awakening
tracks.desc: With tense chords hovering and decending, growling cellos and keening violins weave a dark and rueful melody, echoing timpani add thundering, cruel punctuation.

tracks.title: The Fiction
tracks.desc: Pounding, flanged piano lines echo, clang and swirl into themselves, fading as dark drums rumble strings come in with urgent, scratchy lines and fad as the rumbling rhythms dwindle away.

tracks.title: In The Cold
tracks.desc: Keening synths fade as a cymbal beat and throbbing cello bring a dark rhythm. Bells and synth noises add tiwchy accents.

tracks.title: Muted Fear
tracks.desc: Apprehensive string lines creep as reverberating kettle drums burst like bombs in the distance. The strings play a mournful melody as synths echo with a demonic breath.

tracks.title: Never Look Back
tracks.desc: Creaking hinges and rattling noises echo as ghostly effects slither and shiver. A shackled, wicked door shuts with a bone-chilling clang.

tracks.title: Pulsating
tracks.desc: Dark drums and an evil synth arpeggio build a dark rhythm, folorn piano spins an eerie melody as a churning cello groans and growls.

tracks.title: Sad Story
tracks.desc: Morbid piano lines wander, zooming synth sounds add dark punctuations, searing strings add taut lines.

tracks.title: Haydn Surprise Symphony (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Elegant strings present a rhythmic and bouncy melody, flutes and orchestra add syncopated ornamentation. The piece is grand and industrious.

tracks.title: Haydn The Clock Symphony (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: This piece moves with a child-like joy, curious and unencumbered. The delightful piece leaps and bounds with an enlightened joy.

tracks.title: Haydn The Heavens Are Telling
tracks.desc: Chorus lifts this compelling piece skyward with commanding vocals, the deft orchestra shadows the voices with dynamic accompaniment and grand flourishes.

tracks.title: Berlioz Symphony Fantastic (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A dynamic work, scaling tremendous highs and sweeping moments of calm beauty, strings lead with a melancholy melody as the orchestra gently adds swelling accents.

tracks.title: Berlioz Symphony Fantastic (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Sparkling harp and trembling strings weave a dancing, energetic melody, the courteous orchestra adds debonair accents and backing

tracks.title: Berlioz Symphony Fantastic (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Gentle, graceful strings weave an emotive melody, rising with growing courage, flute adds poignant accents with a simple poise.

tracks.title: Berlioz Symphony Fantastic (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Horns and percussion bring bold and grand strokes to this effervescent piece, with a commanding verve the bounding orchestra pulses with light and power.

tracks.title: Berlioz Symphony Fantastic (5th movement)
tracks.desc: Bringing the engaging symphony to a climatic end, this expressive movement has an unrestrained force pushing the orchestra to dramatic highs, a church bell signals an introspective moment that leads to darker thoughts. Leaping horns bring a climatic end.

tracks.title: Berlioz Shepherds Farewell
tracks.desc: An imaginative work featuring a warm, swelling chorus and melodramatic strings adding an engaged accompaniment.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Commanding strings lend force to powerful piano chords, the piece settles into a reflective and stunning movement, ripe with emotion and awareness.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 1 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: From graceful and flowing to commanding and brash, emotive strings accompany the incredible piano lines in this dynamic passage, solo violin plays rustic, earthy melodies with determination, from dramatic to kind, the piece sways to a picturesque end.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Triangle announces this dashing movement, playful and curious piano melodies explode and dance, the orchestra comes sweeping in and the piece surges dramatically, whirling before shrinking away in a dark gloom.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 1 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Rollicking piano runs decend with furious intensity, the orchestra responds with resounding blasts, tumultuous and enthralling.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 1 (5th movement)
tracks.desc: A playful and bounding tune, happy and leaping almost to the point of frantic. The mezmerizing piano in the last half of the piece is downright stunning.

tracks.title: Holst Jupiter (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Dramatic horns and pulsing strings add a dynamic push to this piece, the engaging orchestra weaves astute melodies with a heroic drive.

tracks.title: Holst Mars (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Troubled strings and winds weave a creeping, suspenseful melody, warm horns bring dynamic and tense lines, churning to a hair-raising climax. Strident and warlike.

tracks.title: Holst Mercury (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Determined winds with a quirky edge weave uncanny melodies, a lone violin brings suspenseful lines, the invigorated orchestra answers with dynamic flourishes.

tracks.title: Holst Neptune (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: A lonely wind melody slowly builds with a mysterious and lost vibe, swirling with a humid pressure. A mysterious chorus adds a frighteningly dark edge.

tracks.title: Holst Saturn (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Muted winds and brass slowly build to a thundering crescendo, towering with a tense and dizzying feel.

tracks.title: Holst Uranus (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Grand horns weave a bombastic theme, percussion adds dynamic accents, the churning melody builds with an industrious tension. Rising, whirling strings erupt into a dark gypsy dance.

tracks.title: Holst Venus (from The Planets Suite)
tracks.desc: Warm, floating horns weave a heavenly, emotional melody, strings bring an embracing, gentle vibe to the emotive brass. The movement has a languid, waiting edge that burns with hope for release.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 2 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Warm and timorous orchestra weaves a picturesque melody for soft and gentle piano lines, lush and languid the peaceful movement sings with melodramatic grace.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 2 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Keeping in the theme, strident strings weave a dynamic conversation with the propulsive piano lines. The full orchestra swings in with bold strokes and resplendent motif.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 2 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Lilting and melodramatic piano and strings weave an emotive, melancholic motif, rising gently, the piece sways and flutters like a gentle breeze.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 2 (4th and 5th movements)
tracks.desc: A touch of gypsy dance brings an earthy flavor to this emotional movement, descending piano lines and echoing strings weave a dynamic and moody atmosphere, swelling a climax and moving into a thoughtful and mellow ending.

tracks.title: Liszt Piano Concerto 2 (6th movement)
tracks.desc: This final movement begins with vigiorus piano lines, soon joined by the full orchestra, that swells into a triumphant and emotive apex. Grand trills and flourshes bring the fantastic concerto to a brilliant close.

tracks.title: Clarke Trumpet Voluntary
tracks.desc: A sweeping piece with a classic lilting rhythm that pulses with eager anticipation and a light of purity.

tracks.title: Dukas Sorcerers Apprentice
tracks.desc: This magical scherzo bubbles and blasts fueled by fantastic imagination and musical imagery, a spectacular piece with intense dynamics.

tracks.title: Leoncavallo Il Pagliacci On With The Motley
tracks.desc: An amazing vocal leads this epic opera, passionate emotions drip from the fevered singer as the orchestra follows with a Wagnerian leitmotiv.

tracks.title: Leoncavallo Der Bajazzo
tracks.desc: A full choir scales magical heights in this uplifting operatic work, the vocal repeating the words 'ding-dong' sets a slight tension as the choir lifts with dramatic appeal.

tracks.title: Massenet Meditation (from Thais)
tracks.desc: This sacred and loving hymnal breathes with a glowing, ethereal bloom. Reaching sky-ward with easy grace and spiritual illumination.

tracks.title: Mouret Rondeau
tracks.desc: This well-known, welcoming and joyous piece rings with a regal and proud melody. Full of history and hopes for a bright future.

tracks.title: City Evenings
tracks.desc: Chiming guitars lead this happy groove, piano follows the ringing guitar notes. Synth adds poppy accents, rolling bass pegs the propulsive beats.
tracks.comp: Pete Calandra, BMI (50%), Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Daytime Express
tracks.desc: Warm slide guitar and percolating synth drums lead this upbeat and building track. Throbbing bass and distorted guitar weave adynamic melody over the bubbling beats.
tracks.comp: Pete Calandra, BMI (50%), Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Dont Wink
tracks.desc: Punky drums and grinding guitars lead this rave-up, squealing guitar notes accent the grungy rhythm guitars, popping drums and pulsing bass hold down the beats with a happy drive.
tracks.comp: Pete Calandra, BMI (50%), Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Hot Tamale
tracks.desc: A laid-back funky jam with an easy stepping beat and in-the-pocket bass. Funky wha-wha guitar gives a sweet icing to the grooving glide.
tracks.comp: Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%), Pete Calandra, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: I Am A Fighter
tracks.desc: Creamy guitars and popping guitars lead this positive, motivational track, building to a sunny rush on the chorus.
tracks.comp: Pete Calandra, BMI (50%), Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Lets Walk Together
tracks.desc: Ringing guitars weave a melancholy melody, piano lines add to the downbeat feel, rich bass and emotive drums complete the set, making for a dramatic but warm composition.

tracks.title: Lonely Nights
tracks.desc: Atmospheric drum machine and sparkling synths intro this sublimely driving track, synth bass and distorted guitars weave a motivational melody as driving drums kick it up a notch.
tracks.comp: Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%), Pete Calandra, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Maximus The Warrior
tracks.desc: Fat, grungy guitars lead this head-nodding, metallic track. Double kicks and dark, throbbing bass kick the beat around with heavy aplomb.
tracks.comp: Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%), Pete Calandra, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: This Is The Time
tracks.desc: Effected drum machine give a tense, waiting feel as atmospheric synths and ringing guitars weave a dark melody. Bass work off the syncopated beats with a pushy groove.
tracks.comp: Pete Calandra, BMI (50%), Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Dancing With A Droid
tracks.desc: Dark, distorted machine beats and percolating arpeggio weave a demonic vibe, screams in the background enhance the spooky feel. The turgid beat pulses with determination.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Darkness and Shadows
tracks.desc: Hypnotic hand drums, varied percussion and a driving beat envelop both sweet and distorted synth lines that float along.
tracks.comp: Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%), Dean Barrett, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Electronic Glitch
tracks.desc: A persistent beat that gradually builds with distorted bass and percussion moving in and out of the mix as melodic and atmospheric synth lines drift around.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Inside The Fantasy
tracks.desc: Fluttering, distorted percussion and a driving backbeat propel etheral vocals, chordal piano work and drifting synth.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Light Inside The Temple
tracks.desc: Understated percussion and mercurial synth lines envelop chant-like vocals.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Partying With Angels
tracks.desc: Distorted synth lines and pulsating drums drive the beat along steadily and persistently.  Sweet, atmospheric vocals appear throughout and lend the track a celestial quality.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Restless Soul Poly
tracks.desc: Squealing synths, distorted bass, and a steady beat lead to the addition of angular lead lines and deep, pulsating layers.  Instruments fade in and out of the mix as the track builds upon itself.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Robotic Sequence
tracks.desc: A deep, throbbing beat is peppered by alternately bubbling and distorted synth that drifts in and out.  Static and softly distorted synth adds to the atmospheric quality of the track.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: World In Transition
tracks.desc: Ambient noise and sharp synth stabs build around each other with a driving bass line, echoing the sounds of a city street as eerie vocals appear unexpectedly.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Darkstar
tracks.desc: Throbbing horns and tense strings weave a dark melody over filtered drum machine, the rhythm pauses and breaks, returning and renewing the tense feel.

tracks.title: Drones
tracks.desc: Raging, pulsing horns and growling strings weave a unnerving melody as a spurting drum machine bubbles and clanks.

tracks.title: The Platform
tracks.desc: Slow-building strings are punctuated with powerful timpani.  Ominous pauses and slow swells of strings serve to create a tense and dark atmosphere.

tracks.title: The Rescue
tracks.desc: Metallic percussion sputters around orchestral horns and spacey synth.  The rhythm builds as the percussion lays down a subtle beat around the mechanical synth.

tracks.title: Silence of Space
tracks.desc: Dramatic horns and mysterious strings surround clanging percussion and dark synth.  The track is punctuated by tense percussion hits that add to the unease.

tracks.title: Stardust Collector
tracks.desc: Darkly thudding drums and dramatic strings drive glitchy synth and a deep, yet subtle, bass groove.

tracks.title: The Thul
tracks.desc: Eerie bass and foreboding strings are accented by the occasional clangs of powerful percussion.

tracks.title: Timesnap
tracks.desc: Fluttering and metallic percussion peppers a dark synth groove.  Dramatic strings build tension and enter along with a solid beat that lays down a mysterious groove.

tracks.title: War Of The Fools
tracks.desc: Eerie synth and dramatic percussion build tension alongside dark and mysterious orchestral swells.  Percussive flutters and subtly powerful horns add to the tension of the track..

tracks.title: Work To Do
tracks.desc: Noisy, mechanical sounds envelop the track while soft, mysterious strings and ethereal percussion appear subtly.

tracks.title: Wormhole
tracks.desc: Darkly triumphant horns and atmospheric synth drift around eerily.  Distorted guitars and powerful percussion lend dark drama to the track.

tracks.title: Arabian Sights
tracks.desc: Mystical, eastern-influenced strings and winds drift like sand in the desert.  Ethereal vocals and strong orchestral accompaniment provide powerful accents.

tracks.title: Asian Fights
tracks.desc: Booming drums and exotic flutes abound as horns and strings punctuate the track.

tracks.title: China
tracks.desc: Eastern strings and winds offer a mystical melody while subtle percussion holds down the beat.

tracks.title: Chinese Garden
tracks.desc: Gently plucked strings and soft chimes lend an atmosphere of serenity to the track.

tracks.title: The Deserts
tracks.desc: Reeds play mysterious melodies along with understated, primal percussion and mystical strings.

tracks.title: Didgeridoo
tracks.desc: Powerful didgeridoo leads the track as percussion and mysterious sounds drift through with soft orchestral accompaniment.

tracks.title: Entre dos Aguas
tracks.desc: A Flamenco-style guitar leads the track along with dramatic orchestral accompaniment, deep bass and periodic percussion.

tracks.title: Northland Moors
tracks.desc: Plaintive harp and guitar give way to a heroic and sweeping orchestra punctuated by hand drums.

tracks.title: Persian Incident
tracks.desc: Percussive stringed instruments and reeds present an Eastern melody that is driven by powerful percussion with dramatic cymbal crashes.

tracks.title: Ride The Sea
tracks.desc: Dramatic orchestra, sweeping vocals, soaring strings, and driving hand drums lend this track a heroic atmosphere before the entrance of some mysterious synth.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Italian Symphony (1st movement)
tracks.desc: The ringing strings flow with style and grace, hunting horns call with excitement, the cellos rhythmic lines add a motivational beat.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Italian Symphony (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Opening on a more somber note, the composition explores moodier tones, a rhythmic string figure is entwined with sweeping melodies, introspective, yet filled with light and subtle beauty.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Italian Symphony (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Gentle, regal string lines weave an emotive and engaging melody, flutes join in and lift the melody to soaring, grand heights. Uplifting and effortlessly swelling to a grand finale.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Italian Symphony (4th movement)
tracks.desc: A whirling and bracing opening scales to great, rushing heights as the strings weave leaping and rhythmic melodies. The dizzying middle section moves with propulsive strings and spinning melodies, building to a momentous end.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Scottish Symphony (1st movement)
tracks.desc: The piece begins with an elegiac minor-key melody from the orchestra before the violins lead into a modulation into major as the orchestra crescendos.  Powerful horns compliment the plaintive strings perfectly throughout, building great momentum.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Scottish Symphony (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Lilting strings along with cheerful horns and winds drive the major-key opening of this movement.  The sections of the orchestra echo each other as the music moves almost frantically in a highly motivic manner.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Scottish Symphony (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Arco and pizzicato strings open up this movement quietly and poignantly.  The melodies are at times reminiscent of pre-Classical modalism, but with the drama and expressivity of Romanticism.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Scottish Symphony (4th movement)
tracks.desc: This movement begins dramatically with powerfully sweeping strings.  The strings flutter quietly when the horns and winds take the melody, but then explode and drive forward.  The movement is frantic in its pace, with carefully placed dissonances.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Violin Concerto (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A mournful violin leads this piece as the powerful orchestral backing supports the fleet-fingered violin runs.  The movement modulates from minor to major, with impressive scalar and arpeggio melodies from the violin.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Violin Concerto (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Soft horns and strings begin this movement as the violin enters with a sweetly expressive major-key melody.  The violin executes impressive, yet tasteful, runs as the orchestra lends dramatic support.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Violin Concerto (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The weeping violin plays a poignant melody with subtle orchestral backing before the entire ensemble enters a quickly lilting section with the violin skillfully executing dramatic runs.  The violin continues to play quickly and expressively as the orchest

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Fingels Cave Overture
tracks.desc: This famous overture begins quietly as the orchestra slowly builds, stating the melody.  The orchestra continues to rise and fall as the melody is traded between sections of the orchestra.  The overture ends with a perpetually rising orchestra.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Wedding March (from Midsummer Nights Dream)
tracks.desc: One of Mendelssohn's best known pieces, this wedding march features fanfare from the horns, tasteful percussion, and sweet ensemble strings.

tracks.title: Mahler Symphony 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: This piece begins with near silence as the orchestra slowly gathers itself.  As the piece picks up, a lilting melody comes forward as the full range of the orchestra is explored.  The movement slips into silences before re-emerging powerfully.

tracks.title: Mahler Symphony 1 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Soft timpani opens this movement as a dirge-like melody is stated and then traded amongst the sections of the orchestra.  The movement builds slowly before it picks up towards the end with a march rhythm and tasteful use of percussion and horns.

tracks.title: Mahler Symphony 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Powerful strings begin this section as they state a playful melody.  The modulations throughout provide the drama as the sweeping orchestra, with full use of horns and percussion, builds in intensity.

tracks.title: Mahler Symphony 1 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Crashing cymbals, dramatic strings and intense horns begin this movement powerfully.  Booming timpani and fierce strings continue before a lull in which the ensemble plays softly and sweetly.  The piece concludes spectacularly and triumphantly.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Intense and fleet-fingered piano moves through bursts of strings and percussion.  Quick chromatic runs and rapid arppegios from the piano race through with tenacity, with carefully placed lulls in the action providing contrast.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 1 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Soft piano opens this movement and is soon joined by lush orchestral accompaniment.  A rich harmonic palette paints vivid tonal pictures as the piano moves skillfully throughout.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Horns and tense strings begin the movement, before rapid runs from the piano enter.  Powerful and intense piano along with compelling orchestral accompaniment lend drama as the piece builds to a grand conclusion.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 2 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Stormy strings and piano lead this movement as it builds in intensity.  The piano pounds and crashes its way through, with perfectly placed pauses in the dramatic action in which the music develops before resuming its fiery pace.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 2 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Softly sweeping strings and poignant piano usher in a moment of calm in this movement.  The piano plays gracefully and gently, but with understated power.

tracks.title: Mendelssohn Piano Concerto 2 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: This movement opens with tempestuous piano and orchestral accompaniment, but a subsequent modulation from minor to major provides a momentary period of repose.  The piece builds to a triumphant conclusion with powerful piano-playing leading the way.

tracks.title: Dark Flow
tracks.desc: Slow-building swells of dark synth and foreboding strings are accompanied by eerie noise and subtle percussion.

tracks.title: The Dark Side
tracks.desc: Squelching synth and ambient noise lay down an ominous backdrop as ghostly piano and periodic percussion complete this spooky track.

tracks.title: Dark Spirit
tracks.desc: Spooky synth and deep bass create an unsettling mood.  Subtle strings and horns appear to enhance the ominous atmosphere before a brief appearance of darkly mechanical drums.

tracks.title: The Deep
tracks.desc: Percussion clatters and pounds as eerie piano drifts in and out.  Elusive orchestral accompaniment barely bubbles above the surface as the ghostly vibe is maintained.

tracks.title: Exploration
tracks.desc: Haunting, ambient synth and occasional clattering percussion set a spooky scene.  Soft strings and ominous horns appear along with some subterranean acoustic guitar.

tracks.title: Green Waters
tracks.desc: Bubbling and cawing synth conjure up the image of a post-apocalyptic beach.  Ambient noise and dark orchestral accompaniment add to the unease.

tracks.title: Its A Shock
tracks.desc: Furious feedback and frightening synth explode and trail off into unearthly ambient noise.

tracks.title: Run Or Die
tracks.desc: Frightening guitar feedback melts away into a wash of ambient synth.

tracks.title: Scavenger
tracks.desc: A dark, yet lively, groove from the bass and drums is accompanied by orchestral strings and horns.  A spooky synth lead provides a mysterious melody.

tracks.title: Baroque Feelings
tracks.desc: Ethereal keyboards and percussive bells set the tone as dark, sweeping orchestral accompaniment emerges.

tracks.title: Forlorn Cottage
tracks.desc: A plaintive flute carries a timeless melody as mysterious piano, sheets of percussion, and ethereal vocals lend to the mystical atmosphere.

tracks.title: Frosted Keep
tracks.desc: Chimes open the track as melancholy horns and soft guitar enter lending the track a sense of longing.

tracks.title: The Green Inn
tracks.desc: Melodic bells lead lush orchestral accompaniment.  Elegiac vocals add to the yearning atmosphere of this track.

tracks.title: Kill The Thief
tracks.desc: A mysterious melody emerges from the orchestra as thudding drums provide the pulse.  The music creeps around while conveying images of clandestine escape.

tracks.title: Mystic Hood
tracks.desc: A flute plays an enchanting melody with sympathetic backing from the orchestra.  Subtle guitar and cymbal crashes color the mysterious mood of the track.

tracks.title: Nights Rest
tracks.desc: Lush orchestral harmonies support the mystical melody.  Fluttering strings, plaintive reeds and horns allow the music to softly drift.

tracks.title: Old And New
tracks.desc: Dark and sweeping strings set the tone along with subtle percussion accents.  Pregnant pauses lend tension as the deep bass and lush strings float mysteriously.

tracks.title: The Plague Is On Us
tracks.desc: Intense bursts and quiet flutters from the orchestra create tension as a mystical melody emerges.  Fierce percussion and dark dissonances add drama to the sweeping orchestral soundscape.

tracks.title: Beatbox Trend
tracks.desc: Warm synth pads and fluttering drums lay down a smooth groove.

tracks.title: Chainsaw
tracks.desc: An edgy synth lead is backed by solid, mechanical drums and fluttering synth that mimics pizzicato strings.

tracks.title: Come Home To Play
tracks.desc: A driving bass line carries eerie harpsichord and dramatic orchestral accompaniment as the beat palpitates beneath.

tracks.title: Contact
tracks.desc: An insistent beat and an upright bass groove drive some funky electric piano and soulful organ.

tracks.title: I Am Wrong
tracks.desc: A dark and smooth groove from the bass and drums is complimented by some mellow guitar work, subtle synth and piano.

tracks.title: Lounge Port
tracks.desc: Muted trumpet stabs through a dark groove from palpitating percussion as warm synth leads and tinkering piano add to the laid-back mood.

tracks.title: Snow Ride
tracks.desc: Mellow guitars, warm electric piano and ethereal synth drift on top of a smooth beat.

tracks.title: Dance
tracks.desc: A playful Renaissance dance featuring buoyant strings and light rhythms with subtle, yet powerful, horns.

tracks.title: Elven
tracks.desc: A pastoral melody with cinematic orchestration is accented by soft percussion.

tracks.title: Friendly Town
tracks.desc: Fluttering strings accompany a rustic melody in a lush orchestral arrangement.

tracks.title: Game Win
tracks.desc: Regal horns and triumphant strings convene victoriously, accented by cymbal crashes and subtle timpani.

tracks.title: The Harvest
tracks.desc: Sweet harpsichord moves through the tasteful orchestral accompaniment as a mystical melody unfolds.

tracks.title: Lordship
tracks.desc: A timeless melody from flute and harp is enveloped by understated orchestral accompaniment.

tracks.title: The Noblemen
tracks.desc: Strong timpani and rhythmic orchestral figures convey a regal atmosphere.

tracks.title: Pleasant Stroll
tracks.desc: Soft acoustic guitar and harp compliment the rustic flute melody along with subtle orchestral backing.

tracks.title: Time Of Silence
tracks.desc: The joyfully rhythmic melody is complimented by lush orchestral harmonies and some ambrosial guitar.

tracks.title: Traders
tracks.desc: Soft pizzicato strings are the backdrop for a pastoral melody, along with some spirited harpsichord.

tracks.title: Mozart Piano Concerto 21 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Light and playful strings dance swiftly along before the entrance of deflty played piano runs that feature quick trills and sweeping chromaticism.

tracks.title: Mozart Piano Concerto 21 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Buoyant strings play a cheerful melody with modulations to minor for dramatic effect.  The piano enters quietly with a poignant restatement of the melody as the orchestra offers sympathetic support.

tracks.title: Mozart Piano Concerto 21 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Lilting strings and fleet-fingered piano frolic about with joyful intensity.  Shifts in tempo and dynamics add dramatic tension as the piano slowly crescendos to close the piece.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 4 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Light and joyful strings open this piece with a lilting melody before the violin enters with emotive and cascading runs.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 4 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Sweet harmonic textures from the orchestra support the poignant violin as it plays longingly.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 4 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The playful violin is surrounded by sweet orchestral accompaniment as the buoyant rhythm drives the piece to a close.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 5 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Fluttering strings and subtle horns set the scene before the violin enters playing a plaintive melody.  Sweeping orchestral accompaniment perfectly compliments the fleet-fingered violin.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 5 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: The orchestra plays lushly and with dramatic dynamic shifts.  The violin plays a melancholy melody full of sweet arpeggios.

tracks.title: Mozart Violin Concerto 5 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The violin plays a sweet melody with a bouncing rhythm as the orchestra lends subtle power and harmonic support.  The violin builds with cascading arpeggios before the orchestra picks up to end the piece.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 3 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Sweeping strings glide playfully as the French horn plays elegant lead lines with expressive power.  The French horn solo that drives the movement to a close is executed with impressive skill.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 3 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: The French horn plays a graceful melody as the lush orchestral accompaniment fills in the spaces.  Perdiodic shifts in the tonal center and dynamic expression from the orchestra lend action despite the relaxed tempo.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 3 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: A lively tempo allows the festive melody to shine through.  The strings dance as the French horn plays dexterous and powerful lines.  An impressive and triumphant horn lead drives the piece to a close.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 4 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Cheerful strings open the piece in a playful manner as the reeds color the sound.  The French horn plays gracefully and with subtle vibrato as the pleasant melody moves forward.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 4 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: The strings move luxuriously as the French horn plays with subtle power.  The movement flows steadily as the horn builds artfully.

tracks.title: Mozart Horn Concerto 4 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: A bouncing melody drives the lush orchestral accompaniment as the French horn plays with lively power to close out the piece.

tracks.title: Mozart Flute Concerto 2 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Sweeping strings carry the opening of this piece as they maintain a lively tempo.  The flute plays swiftly cascading lines with nimble virtuosity and takes an impressive solo towards the end of the movement.

tracks.title: Mozart Flute Concerto 2 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Lush strings open the movement powerfully and with the entrance of the lilting flute the orchestra plays softly to support the graceful melody.

tracks.title: Mozart Flute Concerto 2 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The nimble flute is backed by strong orchestral accompaniment. The persistent rhythm drives the movement forward as the flute plays swift and skilled lines.  An inspired flute solo draws the piece to a close.

tracks.title: Mozart Eine Kleine Nachtmusik (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Jaunty strings burst forth in jubilation with a driving rhythm.  The violins lead the melody as the ensemble uses careful shifts in tempo and dynamics to add drama to this opening movement.

tracks.title: Mozart Eine Kleine Nachtmusik (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: With a relaxed tempo the violins play a sweet melody as the accompanying strings provide lush harmonies.

tracks.title: Mozart Eine Kleine Nachtmusik (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Regal rhythms and majestic melodies drive this movement as the strings occasionally slip into more fluid phrasings.

tracks.title: Mozart Eine Kleine Nachtmusik (4th movement)
tracks.desc: The spry strings jump into action in this movement as the violins play a spirited and triumphant melody as the supporting strings flutter subtly underneath.

tracks.title: Der Vogelfanger (from The Magic Flute)
tracks.desc: Violins lead the way with full orchestral accompaniment to open this selection before urgent and powerful vocals take over to state the inspired melody.

tracks.title: Duet of Pamina and Papageno (from The Magic Flute)
tracks.desc: Contrasting vocal lines compliment each other perfectly as the dynamic orchestral accompaniment sets the scene.  The two vocalists trade the melody before elegantly harmonizing with one another.

tracks.title: Isis And Osiris (from The Magic Flute)
tracks.desc: A soaring chorus produces powerful and lush harmonies along with strong orchestral accompaniment as dynamic shifts add drama to the piece.

tracks.title: Overture (from The Magic Flute)
tracks.desc: The orchestra comes in strong with triumphant bursts.  A slow build leads into quick, cascading strings and dramatic tonal shifts.  A dizzying array of musical motifs is subsequently explored.

tracks.title: Queen Of The Night Aria (from The Magic Flute)
tracks.desc: Impassioned soprano vocals reach improbable heights as the orchestra softly flutters underneath.

tracks.title: If The Shoe Fits
tracks.desc: A slinking groove from the bass and drums is accompanied by funky wah-wah guitars.
tracks.comp: Scott P. Schreer, BMI (50%), Pete Calandra, BMI (50%)

tracks.title: Callout
tracks.desc: Dark, mechanical drums and skittering percussion are accented by powerful guitar and moody synth.
tracks.comp: Mark Steven Cook, PRS (50%), Louise Carmen Cook, PRS (50%)

tracks.title: Groove Addiction
tracks.desc: A smooth beat and solid bass line drive funky guitars and simmering synth.
tracks.comp: Mark Steven Cook, PRS (50%), Louise Carmen Cook, PRS (50%)

tracks.title: Heart Of Everything
tracks.desc: Soaring guitars support sweet vocals as rocking drums and a driving bass line state the groove.
tracks.comp: Mark Steven Cook, PRS (50%), Louise Carmen Cook, PRS (50%)

tracks.title: Know What Im Thinking
